user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Tinytin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6Ll7ZJzUSA6sNVBoGjaSXWIdgHHa5F-01RZEqQu9YuZ82ol2f=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cool place, it was my first time there. The server and management were super friendly and nice. They seemed to genuinely care about providing good customer service. It was surprisingly empty for happy hour. Patio was great. We picked this place because of the menu, there were so many options to choose from, I definitely want to come back and try different items on this menu. I ordered the jerk chicken bowl which I thought was super cool to have an item like this on the menu. It had quite the kick to it for those who like spicy food. Tacos on the happy hour were decent sized and filling.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOt_Xytnk3CqHYOORy0DlQSUZp3qR8XKEWXgVjZ&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"MORI N.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmh-25mC5oA1PFMMA_52ysg1xmB302WDBqAM9LeMqrXCsb_9pPTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Nope. Keep walkin'...

Even if you're super easy going and laid back....
For The Love of Every Burger. For the Love of Every French Fry….
You're gonna wanna skip this place.....I'll tell you exactly why.

Don't let the pictures or the presentation fool you. After your very first bite...you'll know what's up.

The Salmon Burger:
Beautiful presentation, but after the first bite the bun completely disintegrated and fell apart into chunks...now I have just a mouth full of mayonnaise. Not even tarter sauce but mayonnaise. Management cutting corners on the sauce and on the bun. They served you the cheapest bun they could find on the market, and with that said....of course mayonnaise instead of tartar sauce, and we both know which one is cheaper, right?
Now it’s just a pool of watery mayonnaise with what looks like chunks of bread on my plate…it was as if witnessing the incredible science of sponge absorption in action :/

The Garlic Fries:
It looked and tasted like someone else's leftover fries they didn't want, and served to the next guest. It was scrappy, old and cold with barely any garlic. They're even cheap 'ing on the garlic! I told our waiter, but unfortunately it was not much different the second time around.
There is a very loud and clear feeling that management is cheap....with their sauce selections, low quality buns and serving of leftover fries.
The only thing that is not cheap are their menu prices.

Ok...imagine this for me....
You buy a Louis Vuitton bag and they hand you a COACH bag (no offence to COACH)...you know what I'm getting at.....

The Man's Man Burger:
Beef patty was very dry served with cold fries.

Our waitress was friendly, but personally I think even she knew she was serving shit food. Sad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNh5WsccUmi93vii4OXtpvCmHBLQzEv2wL4CwmA&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Champagne Kingdom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT9L6nbhgKeVF6uvC80gh6he8ZgVExYxBb0bRQFJovbeiruBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We kicked off our day with brunch at this lovely spot, arriving right at opening time as their first customers. We indulged in a couple of refreshing mimosas and savored the delicious Eggs Benedict. The seasoned potatoes were a standout, absolutely divine.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsyF8g5nOxpJAloflT70g9NC6qRQjZmQPedH7I&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Negar Shahraji","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgeXxsLnBDqZzY-MsI4B9-Ms6SxHlwc9Nqk9_bYD2kdjeef54=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I have had a lunch and two times breakfast there. Everything was fine, there was only some little things that I didn't like.
When the server brought coffee for me there was no tea spoon with it and the coffee was cold. But generally it's a good place to heads to sometimes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPK3aJtsHnDIYWMMkwkdVme_S7_U7H2jQyXlFew&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Sahil Patidar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUDcDdza4KUNiCiawEL4mIdhAw8-KBIW2vv-EfGXX6eYKYc9Ic=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place serves the best burgers and fries I’ve ever had! The patties are juicy, the buns are fresh, and the fries are perfectly crispy every single time. Their attention to quality and flavor is unmatched, and they always get the balance of sauces just right. The service is friendly and fast, making every visit a pleasure. Highly recommend this spot—it’s my go-to for a satisfying meal!"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karen Tello","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVx32rcWypBnQdQzHSxIPy-G-0rrATiXNsT_bdO6PPseZrzK2vv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Came here for dinner with my friends. Server was knowledgeable and friendly. Other than that, would not come here again. Firstly, the jug of water that was brought to us was white and when the server noticed us staring at it, she said it was “settling”, after around 5 mins it became less white but still did not look right and when we tasted it, was completely off and tasted like metal or something. I ordered the magic mushroom burger and the burger was completely dry, and it barely had any mushrooms and was lacking any flavour whatsoever. My friend ordered the wagyu burger and it was even drier than mine and absolutely overcooked. Will say the only decent thing about our meal was we upgraded to yam fries which were good. I was pretty shocked as this place claims to have award winning burgers. My other friend ordered the Thai curry bowl, which claims to come with chicken and shrimp. This was the smallest portion I’ve ever seen. I was pretty shocked at the tiny little amount of rice that was in the middle. Came with 2 shrimps. Was extremely disappointed our meal and would not come back here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhnhLwcnKGg0rS7K228AR01bm80QelyRZ3Xjy-&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Andrea Pino-Olivares","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDHfW5CQIShXG0Q2Pw9uW-j6d53mSzuaPbenQG8OgvnErBa6_0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Updating my review from two years ago:
Extremely slow service despite being almost empty.
Ordered a burger and fries. They were terrible. Fries were the frozen type and had been reheated. The onion rigs also tasted reheated. The salad was decent. The brunch plate was OK.

Old review: Excellent veggie burger and rice chicken bowl.
Friendy service. Nice atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9J4mwOeORklBY7sMTvW2G1iJjnhDp0UW4Rfy4&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2022-11-21"},{"Name":"M Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJi4yGvZ0EIiVvGbJvBEwvfQZdCqEuSHad_kcYBnGNV_aeLYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Came here when they first opened and have not been back.  Since they have DOV 2024, I thought to try it out again. Wow,  what a mistake.  Took over an hour to get our food. There were only 9 tables of people (at most 4 people per table) at 1325. Can get same quality burger somewhere else for half the time and service would be more prompt.  Asked for the dessert to be packed while we were 1/2 way through our lunch,  but still had to wait for it after we finished and paid for the lunch.  Had one hour free parking but ended up paying more to park as food took so long. Not lying,  but never coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWMySOm0ui-af0aLaWloWb8fKJGGS-YNZu1IPL&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-2-3"}]

[{"Name":"ladan ghafouri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQKWEx_YV_Uj80v-xctgsLSGRY6V78hw5KMb4aNvRdZAaXJWti=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just ordered a salmon sashimi to go. They still gave me a tea while I was waiting which it was so nice . The place was clean and cute. The staff was supper friendly . I have to come back for dine in and try sushi’s .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7GWo-gOrH8uM63b_B_F68bH9-YniYVWntxRQl&fid=0x0:0xbb09970b356e8bd1"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Jillian Cooke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoVfvJseO-GDVyhUvIYpYrM3gIEu4XOG85NMAPmMxfGgxUPF74=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my go-to sushi place! I used to come here because it was close to my apartment but the more I ate at other sushi restaurants the more I genuinely wanted to return and eat here  instead. They are very affordable, but have nice  rolls, great special rolls and delicious sashimi. Best price for a split tuna and salmon sashimi ever, and it tastes great, super fresh. The only thing I've enjoyed more at other restaurants are the California rolls and agedashi tofu. Both are still good here but I've had a bit better.

I almost always get my food to go because it's a small restaurant and I live nearby but you can eat inside. They have an enclosed patio for extra space. Everyone working there are genuinely so nice and my food is ready in no time, usually 15 mins or less. The combos come with miso soup, which is always a nice surprise. I have been eating here at least once a month for years and I have zero complaints. I would like to try their all you can eat sushi one day!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtcorbRSzgNzlHlqlKDdVNWvUBJ99Ya4qaCEK6&fid=0x0:0xbb09970b356e8bd1"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Izmet Barranco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiQo1jy483UmDOGk0DLpOPmwFqDxOxzKBlrj-9MTXzn_Zhoww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We discovered this place by chance. It is kind of hidden in a mall but is is really good. They have both regular menu and all you can eat menu. For the second one they make sure you understand their policy and serve the order in stages, to be sure there are no waste.

Everything was fresh and tasty. Specially mention to the Alaska roll. We absolutely love it as well as the special spicy rolls. A place worth of visiting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVp9Mau4dS68ktoXdSXV7xz-zFjCacsMXDt2pA&fid=0x0:0xbb09970b356e8bd1"],"When":"2023-9-10"},{"Name":"Joanne Antoniak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTQwhPcO13h_HhVjJVUrwpHjU5MeesKhPrxV5pA1ymdZ1edFkY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time visit.
We chose all you can eat sushi lunch. It is expensive ($30/person); and there are some restrictions - but it was SO YuMMy!!
We ate all we could eat 😂
Service was outstanding!!  Our server was attentive and very polite.
Decor was OK; for a very tiny place - but the open storage shelves with boxes on display - affected the atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKlNAzbrATLvfGInUXjueg-i3Q3ErnrlLYtWfg&fid=0x0:0xbb09970b356e8bd1"],"When":"2023-7-8"},{"Name":"D A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJdDPdKx70IF8qinpqf4kBE0d__A91KC9IDnKHhcfzU8QrgaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Not bad food, however, not a place you would go back. Bento bix chicken teriyaki,. Sauce was pre made container sauce,  spring roll was all roll no spring   tempura was 3 x as thick as should be . Temp prawn was sliced to create 2 pcs. If your hungry go but don't expect much. Clean and polite.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dan Peterson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbNeFUlLkRmjcX25zxpAW7H_0IDjY0P_SfdPGvxnigSNv-OQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Sakeya appears to do extensive takeout sushi business and I can see why, I tried the oshi aburi negitoro sushi and the Victoria roll (yam tempura and avocado) and both were very good. The bento box dinner was a good value but the teriyaki chicken was just ok, same for the tofu teriyaki.
We ate in and the service was terrific, our waitress was very friendly and efficient. The atmosphere is casual.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhJaTCegoSjLy_9kfGuFOwBpg3pn0p14-Uk5o7&fid=0x0:0xbb09970b356e8bd1"],"When":"2023-7-1"},{"Name":"Amelia M. Yousf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5xlAQxZMLRLMPVJkxhQxpJn0yTNpaHks1oV_-PENgOE2Kqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My go-to sushi place in BC is wonderful! I used to go there about once to twice  a week, take my food, and head to Rocky Point. They can deep-fry anything! I absolutely love this place and the staff. It's been a year since I've visited, and oh, I miss it so much. I will be back in BC soon, and I can't wait to return! I encourage everyone to give these lovely people a try.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A.J. [{"Name":"Champagne Kingdom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT9L6nbhgKeVF6uvC80gh6he8ZgVExYxBb0bRQFJovbeiruBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hadn’t visited Browns in a while, we our stooped at the Port Moody location reminded us just how fabulous it is! The atmosphere was electric, with great music and an awesome staff. But the real showstopper? Their happy hour specials are to die for! We’ll be back sooner rather than later.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM08OgiuTJ_gmAHVxi34xnNQbshx7yVFh6UhLUu&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"Zane Erickson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyuKKqkuzKUW-9qhJLQJt0mrgnRDbjpiqRvzzVywhPy_mBE3VuhQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brown's in Newport is a great choice, the food is always consistent and delicious, the Cod bowl was kinda disappointing not that anything was wrong with the dish it just didn't pop in flavor like the rest of our choices on this wonderful family outing.

Surprisingly our son Thorne was a big fan of the food which means we have another spot approved by our little tiktok famous son with Autism

As a family with a child on the spectrum perspective the staff were super courteous and friendly and gave ample time for us to choose our dishes and enjoy the evening.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN71nFYx5aQTFkHKijpO9b7rL84O-4Wcz5LZv90&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"ZuffaLtdDanaWhite","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6gGe3NbbgwlJVAvgbTW4PyVUNZSvDx9TwIaijDSbPkD-WMrs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Nachos were not layered. Who  enjoys 75% dry nachos after eating the properly layered nachos on top layer?

I had a dragon bowl with chicken and no rice. The chicken was surprisingly minimal & small bits, and was very dry. Told the waitress and she said she’d let the kitchen know. 30mins pass and I consume the meal. No discount offered or more chicken offered. I was told it’s portioned and precooked etc etc. When Coquitlam Grill offers better quality than browns, there’s a big issue and disconnect.

As well the restaurant was very hot. Had asked if they can turn on the A/C , and there were no changes after that. 110% will not be returning this browns anytime in the near future. Zero tip for the waitress as well who didnt take notice we’ve been sitting for more than 20minutes and wanted to leave. Stood up and requested my own bill. Poorly trained individuals regarding customer experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maisa B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxPIGyNNTj-i7NTQOG0RMWoi-i0VUuEDd6Ah6VVcaDHVppQUA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely amazing spot. Staff is extremely friendly and the food quality is impeccable. 10/10 recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4cInyluIbAQu8HEsrpYNaj6z9DwHXJC0MerA4&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2024-4-30"},{"Name":"Nathan Chang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULis9x-C7u8jouJ6bmV-m7Mb2r-esn5uJaOqGwjwAA9z2MADUV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little spot for lunch. The burger was good and the garden salad was a nice touch versus my usual fries.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTJMryLAfcXBI407jaP9TU9QnQwqR-h3nUsOiH&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRwpWAz0-Yg4cI6ZsOAY9CncZqRN4a6o8nP7KlskI9G71qjLadgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great meal with my friend here couple days ago . Was busy and baseball was on .

Service was great and food came out quickly . I had 1/2 portion of blackened chicken with fettuccine 😋 and my friend had vegetarian addition of the butter chicken which was tofu and cauliflower in the sauce with Nan bread ..

Patio was a nice addition however, we stayed inside the AC as it was hot 🔥 🥵

Definitely recommend fir socializing and having great foods and drinks 👌","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBy0Spz_jKXP1Lpf9_813Q1HhPJkEKEqXfWP0k&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2023-8-20"},{"Name":"Brendan Brow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-7ceZ_7XCL90JLiUO3RxwJE88N3jZDvILaa01EdZkONVmGLlcEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Really disappointed with the experience we had, since previous times here were always fairly good here.
We were a party of 3, ordered an appy and then main dish each. Two main dishes came out while mine was forgotten. When the server finally asked the kitchen it was discovered they didn't get the order for my food. The server comes over to say she punched it in, but for some reason the system didn't send to the kitchen (?). So ended up waiting 25/30 mins more for my dish while the two other people at my table almost finished their meal...
Mistakes happen, system glitches, whatever the case. It's more important how the restaurant manages and deals with the mistake. In this case, it was a kind of blaming the system (or the kitchen?) and absolutely no suggestion or mention of anything to compensate for the hassle. Wasn't worth it","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Golnaz J N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwh094AvMjRiNSQoo9HjnFTPUMh8c3XSGOFZ78okUlI4KLdqnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We dined in the patio. It was a nice space with great food. I asked for lettuce wrap burger. I did try Smokehouse burger. If you like caramelized onion and bacon with your burger, that would be a good option. We got a social red bottle, Jackson,-Triggs, as well for $30, which is a dry one, Cab-Sauv.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbHb-OSUAjT08krqIA6Iur-FY_S4Uh1dRaEIoU&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2023-5-17"}]

The beef dip and fried chicken are great too. 9$ beef deep for lunch on Saturday what a steel. We will for sure be back soon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLDf6O9LafErSU__UlwJfzVp422-1k_z1gvScS&fid=0x0:0x77f071911dfe4c2f"],"When":"2020-10-18"},{"Name":"Kelvin Stokes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLn7FiYP24q0605Gj2Z1yDXW0dZ3SlJo3JaI-ZfhiipWjRyJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Open to the public, and a rock solid deal! There’s public parking in the underground , accessible through the alleyway - it’s not obvious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoA39qMtKiOua__eiDqqJUEJCdssaLJtRtaBx5&fid=0x0:0x77f071911dfe4c2f"],"When":"2023-6-10"},{"Name":"Lauren St John","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWi3pWsd_jh8y8V1Pl7XbMiNRgCVHq-YYCdAOx_KkkOFRnXREk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful new building with a large sports bar/pub. Nice menu selection too. Definitely going back to support our Vets and get in on that Friday night meat draw! Might even try the prime rib. A great place to meet friends and keep the Legion alive and thriving.
#legion119 #veterans #poppies","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSFFtnOOio3jP_zD1v4RXDVFdW9mWMEGfPlJNI&fid=0x0:0x77f071911dfe4c2f"],"When":"2021-8-20"},{"Name":"Topic Agency","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKpLLmZe30kR5QlxEDJSc9OB6UoCkCiJ_ljw6wLVtZQ95LU1Dl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"In this case food is N/A since I didn't eat there.
But the atmosphere and service is splendorous. They do really try their best to help you out","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Seal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtMAHOd6mtXBgcB_lHWdGzTGLOBoxuY3y2CgmbFyFldvb9ZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"[Service scored low due to water policy Vs. 5 star interaction.  We will not spend money on food due to policy.]

We came to this Legion to attend a Saturday night salsa dance event.  We regularly attend Legion dance events in Vernon, Enderby, and Salmon Arm.  Ar these smaller events, water and coffee is freely available. With the same entry fee, and four times the attendees, one would think the Port Moody Legion would be supportive of the event.

On arrival, before the event start, I went to the bar to order two beverages, along with glasses of water. I was informed that management had just instigated a policy of only selling bottled water. I have run across this policy before, when one is only requesting water. I have never been refused water with a meal or a beverage order before.

To reinforce a poor management decision, the manager chose not to be available for the inauguration of this policy.  This is unfair to the employees, who must face the sour customers. Luckily, the bartender had good customer service skills dealing with the unfortunate position he was placed in.  I guess the bartender will either find a better establishment for employment or become the manager at this Legion.

We will definitely not be recommending that our Legion friends drop into this branch.  It will just be a story of how good we have it at home!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shannon Craig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkcCTiYPJx6mTtL4cFio0D_2WqDJBVB2_sRqMM-Qko3xx7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Enjoyed my experience at the Port Moody Legion. Server was very friendly. Food and drinks were not only delicious but VERY well priced. The chef even came over to check that we were enjoying the food. Great experience all around and will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBedwV8VWdv3pw4wwLVfcwKiN0yMnFkRS4VXA&fid=0x0:0x77f071911dfe4c2f"],"When":"2023-2-25"},{"Name":"Kalwant Sandhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWKjft0leBsdm_kFX5OSZ15NI1FCR9f_lQ0muJx87U2uNDsgSRfA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very nice location to drink and dine. Awesome prices, food and service. A great people place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnnrLznU1ggjGvjX4bJdCVV9s0Vu-yuDGQGMZN&fid=0x0:0x77f071911dfe4c2f"],"When":"2022-5-28"}]

They were decent, but nothing out of the ordinary. However, I really enjoyed the cheddar flavor—it was new to me and definitely stood out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTWIC6VC49TZUu9GZ3GYVoFbCoWrxDwMHlARnl&fid=0x0:0xb5bfb1a4bfbe095a"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Sam wins Wells","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNKFEGfgiabHv5G1ZHjQRt6ipm1Q83CrIF-CqaqVVHOkCl5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down, these are the BEST chicken wings I’ve ever had. From the moment I took my first bite, I knew I was experiencing something special. The wings were perfectly crispy on the outside, juicy and tender on the inside, and packed with flavor in every bite. The seasoning was spot-on—bold, balanced, and absolutely mouthwatering. I’ve had wings at a lot of places, but nothing even comes close to the perfection of these. If you're looking for the best wings, stop searching. This place is IT. Simply the best!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXoz-baxNsPwu7qynyE9dLI-RMCVYrLt2nqwVE&fid=0x0:0xb5bfb1a4bfbe095a"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Kim Cuenca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjaWn84n5WkNIiuTVVUDNGG11BZFZ9bDL7ozRG9Qhg3XlrHg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is so good. The wings are amazing it makes me crave more. The burger that I ordered is perfect for my taste!

Our server, Ange, was so accommodating, attentive and friendly. She helped us with everything and helped us with everything we need. We were satisfied and happy with our visit here at Wings Port Moody because of the food, the service and the place was clean and cozy.

Thank you, Ange for the amazing service!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGjptqH3FdoeLfdSjPWQygL5KEsM_ui4pClg77BekGUD0E-Q_8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food took a while to reach our table. Except for Buffalo and Jamaican wings, all the other options in wings are just dull, but I'd recommend Buffalo and Jamaican wings. Tacos were the highlight of the day. They were out of a few drinks and dips on Saturday. Would still recommend it for Bobby Wings.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDaEmmsxSYTd0KqHG1GGK0aJGND6mrDEPlEcUP&fid=0x0:0xb5bfb1a4bfbe095a"],"When":"2024-4-25"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It's surprisingly spacious once you're inside and they have everything you can ask for in a restaurant with a bar, dance floor, live music, and multiple TVs for your favourite game.

The servers are all very friendly and accommodating and the food is about what you would expect from Wings. It's nothing to write home about, but you don't always go in for the food.

I love their beers on tap, cheap wings on Wednesdays, and the electrifying atmosphere on important game nights with friends and family! It's a place that I will be coming back to every now and then.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbZhiNL7Ym7AJ4ZwM2Khlle_b114KNn5wnJGGb&fid=0x0:0xb5bfb1a4bfbe095a"],"When":"2024-1-22"},{"Name":"Heather Bain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGP_U6RMLGGjNkwmYwdhJeH4dP9HKVXM2EwtwgIA4QjU4ZDIk2Yw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I would like to give them a better review but I am not.  Was a last minute change in a freinds bday party. Glad they could accommodate on short notice that is the one positive thing. But it was a Saturday night and busy of course, and they were short staffed. Drinks were mediocre which is a personal opinion. Food was good.  As in short staffed they service was a bit slower than usual. When I am comparing to other Wings locations I've been to before.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marge F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLj5_g_9SDwBb15hkYb6s_LfRvp-45OrDfymdcrjkixQvwaBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So nice to come to a place with the friendliest server I’ve ever had! Lizzie was exceptionally attentive and was extremely helpful as we tried to decide on our dishes and drinks. We tend to take a while before choosing, and she was really patient. The food was great! We had the Texas fries, and they were yummy and filling. The bartender had a smile on his face the whole time we were there, too. Great job all around to the server, bartender, and kitchen!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shane Mccardle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9o-BfnrXqKRNH6NQDfADrksnTzHWsbz6WF8sXz3aqRfIeh0Fp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great flavour choices of wings.
The wings were average, though. I would hope that a place known for wings would have different wings other than the standard kind found elsewhere $18.5  per order for average is tough to swallow.  Service was great for our party of 25 to 30 people, and the server hustled and did great and was very pleasant and same as the food runner.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Avis Woo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXh4Pb-SJt2DTMUggN2-tIRxEo8pAErRU5SI_TxM4gC-gvdVBym=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for family brunch and dinner! Dishes all come in n big portion! Coffee refilled unlimited times! Tables and environment is hygienic and seating quite spacious and comfortable even for senior citizen with backache like me. Toilet is clean! Waiter and waitress crew are all very nice and professional too! Love this restaurant very much❤️❤️❤️❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPza0ew2GjCDcnw3yaVoLhK8iMmk0FFxjlS2rw5&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"Kai-Chun Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjTiDNcTKlmyRrDWdGPFt530dlO3QJbviz_GUObBc3bQ0rNmRp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of my favorite restaurants in Coquitlam as it's a place where I'm guaranteed to have a good time.

Food - the food isn't the most amazing thing I've ever tasted, BUT every single one that I've tried was at least good or better. There's basically no bad choice in the menu.
Service/atmosphere - the seats are spacious and comfortable, the waitresses are always friendly (even more so to kids!), we never had to wait too long for our food... it's just a great experience all around.
Price - with the above points, it would've already been one of my restaurants of choice, but then they went ahead and kept the price reasonable and that just seals the deal for me.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN90L9zlD4vK0EDnXwB3NnlbNYPDfIUE5NcHqHh&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Omid Dadgari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXY5oTTgmTf1M1XQYNbrrLX-SdVGDzUB3Iw3aDSyAgQLf2_BwYgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I visited Coquitlam Grill for breakfast today and ordered Steak and eggs. The overall quality of the ingredients was very good. However, I ordered my steak medium, but it arrived well-done. Despite this, the quality was still good. The quantity of the food was very generous, offering great value for the price. It made me full, even though I hadn't eaten dinner or supper yesterday. The servers were attentive and friendly. The atmosphere was typical of a North American restaurant and quite enjoyable. Overall, a decent experience with room for improvement on the steak preparation."","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNT61QeH3ufJtT_GqPt1Sg0rufpTlP24BeUhlEu&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"Julie B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4pd43YT5KSqkORSPaVbra7_KcodZ1kkwID5yaolZD_WuCOEiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What an amazing restaurant. We went just after noon on a Sunday only waited a few minutes and were seated. The place was packed. Everyone thoroughly enjoyed their meals and beverages.
Food was Ultimate Omelet
Mexican Pulled Pork Hash
Tex Mex Omelet
Eggs Haida Benny
Drinks were margarita, mimosas and a Ceasar.
The service was fantastic and Susan was amazing.
Everyone raved about their dishes and everyone cleaned their plated and both styles of harsh browns by far were the best we have ever had.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNatRTF11J76msxdL31ksun0mlD6h6LFwhaBmNW&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-7-30"},{"Name":"Thomas Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUITuDRjw9J9Us45xAUXKSfp8lG2sJ2s04TW_lNAi_G6a5d62ur=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Just came here for a dinner. Thought it was good overall. Satisfactory but not amazing. I had the steak and it was cooked nicely. I wouldn’t rush back because the value isn’t very good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJH7QVel_maomATRS9LUNPh_6vm10Rj-xcyjR2&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Rakin Hassan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXandqMb5qdp3U7pCkKHH5i5AInuGc7KeC3c0mJR9W6MOUUvQAlEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Don't order the turkey dinner if you like flavor. Its all just a big mush. If there was a physical representation of the emission "sadness" this would be it.

Ps had a taste of my friends burger and it was one of the best ive had. So Im sure their other items on the menu must be good, just not the turkey dinner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqodY3fX-WlUgRDwc2Piqi1n1ENVZQ-jAmw5hR&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Gaelen Norman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBHJXfwZ66Qec82NI1asE8mxzV5EwKVb0vYtF7rcjFlBcha36q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's exactly what you expect for a little greasy spoon. The Friday special is my favorite. Ribs and spaghetti for $26.

Service is good. Free refills on pop. Good food. Just what you need","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtZLYC7SXtZ97JI0Cb02o_4Sii4vdAzTdKrt9i&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Amir Zadmoghadas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqdew5KhFVD5RxOgB382TX7EpmHMMi0CV5o3h8uilBWfKyE8w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"great experience with friends at this wonderful restaurant. Thank you for all the excellent service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHZ5toNPIibXswgykxegtY3Ax23juUgo7gz5X3&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-11-12"}]

[{"Name":"Jeff Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVeVKpdfNOdTnoZ-ITkSuOW-c2zXalTP1RiXc0xiQ5ZEZBSpWaGw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Perfect shawarma, super nice people! Meat had great flavour and generous portions! We got the mix platter but we preferred the chicken slightly more (though the beef was still good). Great option to bring over to the park to eat!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQzJvcz8PRjcYdOnZx06UAeEQnRtgFFmzPVHYh&fid=0x0:0xc0fa752af0315d0b"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"Michael Dufour","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRJlumZmuYhT1sl7gSM1UjM4Th7vqT40yNCUCsqnXE3Nr0wA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Might be the worst Shawarma I’ve had in Canada. So much salt on the beef we could not finish it. Pita portion was half (a pita, which was fresh), rice was 5/10. Sauce portions were 2 teaspoons each of hummus and garlic sauce. Salad was all lettuce  and two sad looking turnips.
I’m super disappointed. I have passed the truck outside my work downtown several times and have been anticipating trying it. Did not expect it to be so, so bad. Bad enough to compel me to leave this review.
Staff working the truck were wonderful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ridhwaan Murad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZ01NrIJq-bXx2O0TQQ_Nlv3d1BmJDfMG1zJNirVKOrJxl9RtiBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best shawarmas I have had in some time. I usually get the number 2 which is the Arabi king sandwich made with saaj bread.

Authentic shawarma from back home and recommend it if it’s your first time visiting. I have also tried some of their other menu options and enjoyed them as well.

Service is great and owner and employees are always friendly and welcoming. Definitely worth trying you’ll end up coming back again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"mai shahein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoxDyrxkAT0ypuXV1luJ_1yS8iOBJ7ApSOx5JcLXUjwx0Gzw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The beef shawarma had a lot of chewy stuff that doesn't cut, chicken shawarma is good but not the best, however the falafel is really great","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sathiyaseelan Suhashini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGCDhZwAvUF3Q8iMEpEx8TQCvKbwiXzYFJN0uOrenEt7v0wxGX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst Arabic bread Shawarma. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"1961pocoloco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUbZ9PaXJo4xzkoAqh4HXKfKgRZ-9UZ_Ejcd0meZuO8sfAVA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was excellent, great service and a very clean restaurant. Butter, chicken, lamb, curry, Mariani rice, curried calamari all were excellent.
No need to drive into Vancouver anymore for this type of food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMF0BTwhAg7PfswQh1pM6oJ8WOC0K4ozUBmqE6c&fid=0x0:0xf7cc60cb2ceeb0c9"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"Luke Weng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn1tdfwXfRnZVszKV8bZBNwooyRqfHv0VT8T0EAQWyUrqTrrO6aQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place. Right when you walk in, the ambience is just dimly lit and romantic. They even have a mini waterfall fountain.

The staff were very nice and welcomed us to our seats. The menu was a bit expensive with the smaller portions, I kind of wish there were more curry, but the naan were huge! 😁 Our server even checked on us to see if our food was good.

We tried chicken korma and goat vindaloo. It was my first time trying goat. It tasted just like beef.

They even complimented me on my goose bag hehe. The food here truly was aromatic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpezuMfXVR8AEDTaKJahH_EyKMlXciBIXx3mBO&fid=0x0:0xf7cc60cb2ceeb0c9"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"ladan ghafouri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQKWEx_YV_Uj80v-xctgsLSGRY6V78hw5KMb4aNvRdZAaXJWti=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The place had such a traditional design . The food were awesome . Garlic bred was on the other levels ! I wish I ordered more of that to take home","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOt1dHtwturR6P635mytr9pgcw99Nfcf1NrmqpZ&fid=0x0:0xf7cc60cb2ceeb0c9"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"JASON HESAMI","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0dODtY3FfG-gz2R-VCX2ZoLKUTq3QRvoiyA0R-nt2IO46qbjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’m not saying the food was not good!!!
Or there was a plastic strip in my dish!!!

The thing is when I took back the food for exchange, they accused me that put it there intentionally, while as you can see still 80% of food is there!!

I’m saying don’t go there if you respect yourself.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEGIOMZUq1LANLVFAaJ6ySINuCgFHEEKY0uA5Z&fid=0x0:0xf7cc60cb2ceeb0c9"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Dorothy Zor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvcdoDZaEuwDxmTo3VbyJqqMtqX4SaUalqwxeAtvqlISApNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is our favourite Indian restaurant.
We have been coming for years.
Always fast and friendly service.
Flavorful dishes with the right level of flavor and heat.  They serve good portions and menu has reasonable prices. Restaurant is clean and lots of free parking.  My kids and I love the food here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joshua Carballo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXa7i0JW3U67qEp1_qeXXjwVnk_ZJNofkdzUM4GGNVaSEZnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst butter chicken in the tri cities, probably worst ive ever had anywhere. Sauce was essentially tomato sauce from a can heated up, unseasoned. Chicken also unseasoned and had the consistency of soft microwaved chicken meat. This dish probably reflects the overall dishes at this restaurant. Stay away!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"shwetha Iyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOZy6UyIqB3XpHUKisL_8Jnz84KNTbZg_gesP64h3m4G-CoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We ordered a takeout from this restaurant yesterday. We tried to eat the food as soon as we got it home. The rotis that were given were very hard and so cold. It didn't appear fresh. The curry we ordered was medium spicy but it was made so spicy that we all couldn't eat. Very disappointed with the food. We ended up not eating any of the food. Please look into it and make sure food given is fresh.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gigi D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEdISu4AIzfO-XdFOHc3rbEhSiwRMFcrS0OteyCIfGdbOIIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cute little restaurant. The owner/chef was our host/server for lunch. He was so kind and courteous! We were there for a work lunch, and most of us (including me ) have never been there before. He helped explain the different dishes. We ordered an assortment of dishes. Butter chicken, pakora (delicious) and a few rice dishes and this appy of fish that were coated and I could have eaten the entire plate and 2 types of Naan. we ended with chai tea and this variation of donut.(round dessert with a syrup). I can't remember all the dishes but I would definitely go there again!
give it a try!  I forgot to take photos this time 😕","Images":null,"When":""}]

The Verde enchiladas were nice and spicy with lots of crema and the pork belly bowl was very filling! Having the pork in small chunks made it easy to have some each bite. Our server Alicia was also great!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNavn6xqs3gBtkt2nCsRVoaMp7E_4GNKCfusgU2&fid=0x0:0x3576f9f5b5a0f06c"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I only grabbed quick lunch with a friend, but I already want to go back for more! The chicken burrito had tons of meat and full of flavour with decent portions and price. The server was also very friendly!

I recommend this place if you're looking for a good burrito/taco restaurant in Port Moody area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYLbd8uuN-9MGU07dEVD0rf3wYj7ttpeGaHC0S&fid=0x0:0x3576f9f5b5a0f06c"],"When":"2024-6-17"},{"Name":"Herbert Camat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKXSkcN5npL56jCqrImwFWlxlBsiSCmQ0Pl7fUB01TSYknRkt_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Mexican food in the greater Vancouver area, in Port Moody! I had the guac and salsa with chips, so good! The tacos were divine and delicious!!! But for me, the highlight is definitely was the pork belly bowl! The flavours came together for a great blend into a delicious circus!!! And the margaritas and cocktails they have were also extremely good!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmkU41lBpiL-0cbvA0PS4ROXJFJWzPXMq0N4Qi&fid=0x0:0x3576f9f5b5a0f06c"],"When":"2024-5-11"},{"Name":"liberty facundo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNBp5rH1To4BVHWq1Mfj3iKJNDPtZ8CbWa3yq0RypDCjJicJtkRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried this place for some quick take out tacos and the place was so nice. The tacos that we ordered tasted really good, the fave is the Korean bbq pork taco. Will definitely come back to eat in next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAM89PY2rckTvUkNSWLpXt6Vk2FR_ssdYMX1hc&fid=0x0:0x3576f9f5b5a0f06c"],"When":"2024-8-15"},{"Name":"George Says","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXohTUDS1Hme-40_fBadV_6ZJOt8nYejw_acqYyifv5Fy1T5nx77A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food!

I am for Mexico and I can honestly say that the way they play with the fusion of flavors in this kitchen is amazing.

Super tasty tacos
Great Torta
The sauces are delicious

The service is good although sometimes I think they are short staff for the amount of customers there are.

I would just like to mention one thing, I have been to this place about 10 times, my experience has always been good, but this last time as we had no reservation they put us on the waiting list (which is completely fair) but they made us wait almost 50 minutes, and they seated us at the table that was available when I arrived to ask.  In fact there were a total of 5 tables available, I never understood why they couldn't seat us from the beginning.

We waited 50 minutes in front of the door and the tables I saw were never used 🤪.

Greetings.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwUKZ3pbZedCpK1bDRuB7p_smLnp3LxxZgdw-7&fid=0x0:0x3576f9f5b5a0f06c"],"When":"2024-5-14"},{"Name":"Colton Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9J-0Vx6x8cF5YVvJZsNgZ_ehNWjBzDwqwuFlN_lt9-EfdsJIu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hard to find a critique about Taps and Tacos. Service was amazing and fast. Food came out quick and was fresh and full of flavour. The menu has lots of mouthwatering options that makes you want to order it all.. the drink menu has great local beers from surrounding brewery’s and a very impressive cocktail menu with lots of Mexican inspired drinks. My favourite Mexican street taco restaurant and my favourite restaurant in Port Moody.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPC1xxxC5kQhrk4Y6iodn9J5QJTzJbEi_zlfm62&fid=0x0:0x3576f9f5b5a0f06c"],"When":"2023-6-5"},{"Name":"Ava Quinn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMU8VO2fB7cXmNzEfci_rgw-GMvyqSUc989asfRnFG0burVgIH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got the tacos here one day and the bowls another. Everything we ordered was amazing.

Atmosphere was upbeat and cool with all the glass. The music was insanely loud both days we got dinner though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOe5mxP_vYLi5Nmvc_pUWu7JOVUdEKAsEpW_2UW&fid=0x0:0x3576f9f5b5a0f06c"],"When":"2024-5-14"}]

[{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It's a pretty typical dim sum restaurant with decent food and service. I appreciate the speed of the service and the value for all the food. It can get pretty busy, especially during weekends so be prepared to wait if you didn't make a reservation.

We got the lotus leaf wrapped sticky rice with pork, some steamed pea shoots, vegetable porridge (congee) and good selection of dumplings. It's not anything to write home about, but it's hardy and gets the job done. Solid experience overall and I would give them the thumbs up.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNldHIuVK-fsR57KEsIFq08_KeBGOEZKK1j8FvJ&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Grace Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJv2Qb5BK8BlHD8B-fNqpMIiwBP96of3n6s7qsHpu4xPXVSJg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious and cute dim sum! Food was fresh and fast. We made reservations as it can get busy. Staff were friendly and attentive. I do speak Chinese as well. The kids love the food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqxd3kLGHCrMQedJ1T0fOAbSmVa-M_lHRR3aR-&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"Celina Wright","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXh2wmxFC5Utlekpzdr2MpXFcBCcrOSjcqSIoXPM9bCTR9ROXAVjw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food was fantastic and the staff were polite.  We visited for dim sum on a weekend. Seating took some time (10-15 minutes) even with a reservation, but I find that to be normal at most dim sum restaurants.

For those unfamiliar with a dim sum restaurant: just make sure you flag down the wait staff if you need anything and they'll head over to you quickly - don't wait for them to check in on you.

We had about 6 dishes among 4 people and were very satisfied with all of them 😌

We had an overall great experience and will visit again soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEjZuQIZKRlmVGxE6oDTnZ2lj9iQ_fe2zH2aWD&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Annia Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCmNf-6kVgoV3z2v1rhLUKPIXQtdwZxPsOxdlb6pZhbXP-BQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Enjoying some yummy 😋 dim sum for brunch.

A culinary tradition that has captured the hearts and palates. The term “dim sum” translates to “touch the heart,” a phrase that encapsulates the essence of these bite-sized delights.  So many different varieties of special Chinese dishes, served in small portions for all to share.
Dim sum has always been a symphony of colors, textures, and flavors in each dish to share amounst friends.

Food was fresh and fast service provided. Staff was attentive.  They were busy today luckily made reservations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBhObly0gYODvg08E6vPpciOoSHEghCgOJz5-x&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"K 2","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCr90XQEGh_XW_dogXGAOrNDNdWl4oto2DcQXyO8hGv5A6DKrVWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently had an incredibly disappointing lunch here. We ordered four dishes, but after waiting for more than an hour, only three arrived. The last dish never came despite us repeatedly asking about it. When we requested to cancel the order after an hour, the server responded with an attitude, insisting it was coming. After waiting an additional 20 minutes with no sign of the dish, we had no choice but to cancel it for good.

To make matters worse, the food that we did receive was subpar, tasting like frozen dim sum from T&T rather than freshly made. Seafood roll was.. speechless.. since when the imitation crab became seafood????
The entire experience—from the long wait times to the poor service and bland food—was awful. After spending an hour and a half there and only eating three dishes, I was left feeling frustrated and dissatisfied.

I definitely won’t be returning, and I would not recommend this place to anyone looking for quality dim sum or good service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO797XW5ANvImlqxiyC1g_s4CcDzQenFyWjxZsG&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"J T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhlRzWDXzdsN5IEg7ILK_EQ56zA9jcQ-fPPr3cS5cgV1YVlw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Another Neptune afternoon…

I think this is the only Neptune I haven’t been to yet? Anyways, in the area taking care of some business so decided to try this location out.

It’s located on the front side of Coquitlam Center and facing the new Cactus Club, plentiful of parking is available up front in the malls parking lot.

Inside is separated into to section; Neptune Wonton for fast casual dishes and Neptune Seafood for more of a formal dining. It’s kind of a smaller place and pretty basic to me.

Anyways, here were the dim sum I ordered;

1. Seafood dumpling in soup. The imitation crab being used made the broth a bit overly sweet, was too unpleasant to finish it.
2. Steamed spicy beef tripe. It wasn’t tender enough, needed to steam it a bit longer.
3. Steamed chicken feet with special sauce. It wasn’t tender enough for the skin to fall off the bone, needed to run through the deep fryer a bit longer during the prep process.
4. Turnip cake with XO sauce. It’s almost a joke, my 10 year old nephew could’ve done better with this dish especially its presentation. Failed!
5. Baked preserved egg and ginger pastry. Absolutely horrible, the preserved egg was rubbery and the whole pastry crumbled along with its ginger paste. Failed!
6. Fried vegetables with shrimp paste. An alternate version of the deep fried eggplant with shrimp paste. It was so so.
7. Baked bbq pork buns. It was okay, the bbq pork could be less sweet.
8. Purple rice roll with fish paste. It was okay, the super jumbo size was unexpected.
9. Stir fry udon with live lobster. Surprisingly it was pretty good, enough wok hay to really bring out the flavours.
10. Little white rabbit pudding. Not bad, cute little treats.

Overall, I wasn’t too impressed with the layout and atmosphere of the restaurant. It portray itself as a mid class Chinese seafood restaurant, but felt l like a simple family restaurant with mid level prices.

The service was okay, enough to satisfy the basics, don’t expect anything more than that.

As for the food, honestly it was probably one of the most disappointing experience I had so far out of all the Neptunes I’ve been to.

Not a repeat or recommendation from me anytime soon… 1.5 stars","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQR35TFh2sABn6mWQv4-F7inIjdWxHkqeXqX1w&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Danny Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8eoyUE6az-FmQo7i2mVq5z64Ow48sgKu1EmLZc0zWWN6DMy5asw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came for dimsum. The portions here are pretty big and taste fresh. Lots of menu items to choose from. We had a larger party (11 people) and they had our table ready on time. However they forgot 3 of our items which we ended up cancelling. Overall good food and friendly service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2zar_Z9-rBEtiUz29w_-7yCkOfWbkH7rr9FO8&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2023-10-9"},{"Name":"CY","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyAWoVXS2wSYA_X8YaMHwhMb74Th2juKHatcW6zvf48kBI0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Been here twice, once in July 2024, once in Nov 2024. Quality difference between a couple months was huge. (Much better food quality and taste now).

Clean and spacious environment.

Food was served a bit slowly though.

Dim Sum dish variety is quite limited on the menu.

Price is a bit higher than mid tier

Over it is decent","Images":null,"When":""}]

Mamma Said Pizza is doing it up right - long live the mamma.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoaSwNfsWaTEZXjdcWE8-SN8KBVHupPGsSh2bt\u0026fid=0x0:0x1139f763070a03ff"],"When":"2024-11-8"},{"Name":"Brenda Bodnar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXip0tnc2MAYTd_t7flKkNJ49zhhPh5jcpiZ2opIuOQ4PhmwTrIbw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Saw this place in passing and Googled the reviews before deciding to order a pizza.  It was a 20-minute drive home so it was only lukewarm by the time I got in the door.  Regardless, this was the tastiest pizza I have had in several years.  I was surprised to see a thin crust which is always my preference.  I went for a simple pepperoni and mushroom with green peppers.  What I noticed right away was that all of the toppings were intact large pieces of pepperoni, green peppers and mushrooms (nothing minced on this pizza).  What a unique idea to drizzle honey on the crust.  It was really delicious.  This place is no where near my home but I wish it was.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP16gbvSTOqTrP4dk_LMPnSBdkqjfuRrJp8GMql\u0026fid=0x0:0x1139f763070a03ff"],"When":"2024-3-23"},{"Name":"dididodido dido","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUvYQ6xK6svVdEg35LPnw6_RTbAl1bXcHiT4cUWLK4iYa_WA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent pizza.  Crust is thin, crunchy, without being too hard.  Firm and holds everything together. Easy to fold to stuff your face.  Had the Montreal Special and it had the perfect balance of ingredients and flavours.  Will definitely go back again for more.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marissa McKinnon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVY68LF-WJ3XLlkLB3mmSI9NIX-eNSB4BF4a47z33JIFfXjKyxv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best pizza I’ve had in a while! We chose the BBQ Chicken Pizza (with arugula instead of bacon) and the Fungi Pizza. Employee was very nice, and the pizza was made in a very timely manner. It was made beautifully, hot, delicious and evenly distributed toppings. They also had super cute, festive, halloween decorations up!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQwxkNkBXjxxMK1RNiHCF_YsEAhhxOKbp9Iuw6\u0026fid=0x0:0x1139f763070a03ff"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Derek Carr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXs5_9YoepHwXwJWgv8UG_Z7CMlP5ieqzu0oxCf6nhH4MEO-iM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"While most pizza places that we’ve bought from have become more expensive and less toppings and flavour, this place has absolutely perfect and tasty NY style pizza. The honey butter basted crust is crispy and delicious. Very fresh toppings. Super clean, but not really an “eat in” type of pizza joint. Friendly staff as well. My new “go to” local pizza place for sure.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Toscanny Pandu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2gApUU6OqcgWej11WkI-IMAGjyAEo0RtxkVpTLkvbOK8AwZY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Definitely brought nostalgia back to being in Manhattan New York. We came an hour before closing and all the by-the-slice were cold..but with a bit of time in the oven, was brought back to life. I was pleasantly surprised how good the crust was, it was thin yet crispy and reminded me of what you expect from a New York slice. The cheese was the perfect amount, however the slice could have used a bit of more sauce. Great family atmosphere, and the owner was super friendly.\n\nWill definitely be coming back to get a fresh slice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFYzeyJXcJ64tV9fo1AYX-OLMluTy4a9jkmvdK\u0026fid=0x0:0x1139f763070a03ff"],"When":"2021-9-6"},{"Name":"Jeff Downer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXl3HQ-1C4N-_a7ykvhIi5aM883AB-cDQVYb1xeenCY7zekayvZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered the Godfather of all pizzas. Wanted to try this place for years. Blown away. We were starving and this hit so many spots. It’s exactly what I would put on top of a pizza, only they make it taste better. The crust was a great surprise and the pizza ooozed in all the right ways. Staff totally ruled. We chose to eat in the alley on our folding chairs because it was a nice evening. Would order from here daily if I lived in PoMo!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfgMn1cxZVer8R8f6Qph68H9VTRFTpJJovv-Wr\u0026fid=0x0:0x1139f763070a03ff"],"When":"2024-8-11"}]

title: Mega Donair

[{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"One of Port Moody's Donair shops. Mega Donair has been here for years and I like that they actually make fresh bread (pita) for the donairs by order. Fresh and tasty every time I visit. Air conditioned and comfortable seating inside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYOnB6DnVivYV3LB4cEUVUQQCClxRazx0z9dRK&fid=0x0:0x5e0681c0310f59d8"],"When":"2024-7-24"},{"Name":"Negin Modir","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIxLrD9MaLLUXrRzDgC04oGs7WW9wweZNAc7nLEJ1sx6y-ew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place!! the food is always so delicious and the lamb is super tender. Portions are huge and I believe its the best donair in the city with tons of flavor. The customer service is  also TOP notch! you must try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNO3FnCInyJErXqJ_oaqlbcexkhaLFcFzxlbDvP&fid=0x0:0x5e0681c0310f59d8"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Al So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLumQHIv-5W9wXPr4ZbA1zWCVnPk2w1Kc3bjsO93-VMG-v7JQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you haven’t been to Mega Donair  in Port Moody, you’re missing out! This place is like the Aladdin's cave of donairs, filled with treasures of flavor and freshness. Very yellowly inside...

First off, the pita bread here is so fresh, you’d think they had a team of genies in the back, flattening and heating it up right before your eyes. Seriously, watching them work the dough in the machine and then heating up on the stove like watching an ancient Middle Eastern cooking show – mesmerizing!

Now, let's talk about the donairs themselves. These bad boys are stuffed with ingredients so fresh, they might as well have been plucked from the Garden of Eden. Each bite is a flavor explosion that’ll have you saying, “Open sesame!” for more. And the size? Let’s just say, Ali Baba would need more than 40 thieves to finish one of these beasts! We got the chicken 🍗 one, and was pleasantly satisfied after.

Sure, Mega Donair might not be the cheapest eatery in the souk, but with the quality and freshness of their ingredients, plus the friendliness of the staff, it’s worth every dinar. The service is as warm as a Middle Eastern bazaar, and the flavors will take your taste buds on a magic carpet ride.

So, if you’re in Port Moody and craving a donair that’s fit for a king, head over to Mega Donair.  Your taste buds will be belly dancing with joy!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgrkhj5xVUjAfVjhzyVEHRmpAEg6bBJIxdkiZD&fid=0x0:0x5e0681c0310f59d8"],"When":"2024-6-18"},{"Name":"James Tasker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9NiNIaLm_vJXAOyrHHjnqFvKsK-Y4c4_NtjLMC68D0-TJQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Honestly, I’ve had loads of Donairs from everywhere in the province. The freshness, friendly customer service, and inviting atmosphere make Mega Donair an All-Star Donair. This family run business provides great portion sizes while yielding affordable prices. Would recommend to anybody in Metro Vancouver to come try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPG0C_Tt8T2WntUVhQQVgPq1svg_98gWMqeYBnL&fid=0x0:0x5e0681c0310f59d8"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Robert Horne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjh3uBuk3kJPg-hc-U_wrcI93lKxaVucpTodap5gNstb2Dhe87Uw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best donairs I've had in Canada 🇨🇦.   I always order to go.  only a few tables if you want to eat in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXMC7c-Khv88KH2C6n3eoh4HbkT-jBOagZ5-bc&fid=0x0:0x5e0681c0310f59d8"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Jay Cree","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAhbDuRRifjlCFV-tmlxA3mssdJQPE0JavP0ck4Atsh9-EJM4_8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A rather unique approach with freshly made pita for each donair, you don't see this too often around here and it sure works well. Portions are very generous, I barely could finish the medium one. Great flavor and fresh ingredients.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWRunvmCf7c7N3nqd-amQ-qJNq4kYsHSI1bcpG&fid=0x0:0x5e0681c0310f59d8"],"When":"2022-11-29"},{"Name":"Aydean Mehri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7vsez26Z2HmbRPWHEjpz0jN2LhiuT-gyNLWVk7RTpbV3-1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I heard so much and I never tried it until today while at work

It was so authentic so good so homie, home made bread, Baklava.

The chicken and lamb was seasoned well and Most importantly, it was not greasy or oily, but it was tender and delicious and well seasoned

Absolutely love it can’t wait to go back","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Luke Lindenbach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAnciz0S6b-f06TL37KstoBSdDYL6OxSrD4eSrdLWrj3F3qg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We tried the Lebanese Mega Donair. Very tasty. Large enough to share with my wife for dinner and still have leftovers for lunch. Stuffed full of meat (not just lettuce like they do at subway) will definitely go there again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2qr2Wdn1Cu_5F_NuEuoStKTUtXNC_lsTUKj5L&fid=0x0:0x5e0681c0310f59d8"],"When":"2022-5-31"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Neda G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcXBADLi2CMhn5hf9f-JdbOlYYM_LHhdjb9JmX03VjxzMph4k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The reviews are legit! This place is a hidden gem. We had a lovely breakfast with my kids, mom and husband. The service was good despite only one person working, she did awesome and they were very respectful of my daughter's allergies.

More importantly, the FOOD was AMAZING!!! Crispy gorgeous potatoes, really yummy pancake and waffles and great coffee. Will absolutely go back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZm2JrIJBpWvMNrTgyP1KWz2ol7OXkf14yCZLp&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Cherilyn Morris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFSsTxkRHOvnhVnL21RRcRzjanEDvQ_-BctHEQEFo9i_I6jA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered via a delivery service and were very pleased with the food from PK's Diner. We gave a 5 for atmosphere as we have read reviews stating how comfortable the diner is and therefore had to give a 5 for that reason. We had the Bacon Cheeseburger and Clubhouse sandwich. Both were delicious. My husband said that the burger is one of the best that he has had. The burger was loaded with tomatoes, bacon and onions and he really liked the burger sauce that came with it as well. The bacon was thick and my husband said that the caramelized onions made the burger. I also found my Clubhouse to have been very good also with thick bacon, ham, and a generous amount of grilled chicken. The fries were crispy and the picture with the Clubhouse did not have all the fries that came with the order. We both have left overs for tomorrow. We are always cautiously optimistic when ordering home delivery due to the food not being fresh out of the kitchen. Well, we were so pleased with our meals and will definitely be ordering again. We are looking forward to trying out more items on the menu. Thank you so much PK's.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLTqRnbF0525X_IBQ69XBMilRq6EUKYroOWi1f&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Kim Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIR3fyXypuJm8ILEdOCVPODC97_SULpf89BUpmEUxYYnr0uBA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Breakfast tasted great. I had the smoked duck benedict - delicious, tender duck meat. Fluffy pancakes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQQTCyuOJoSGd_q3QxCrjr06WtsiKzh8wWmmkI&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Khwanravee Phajum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6GF6hlgxdCI-il-sbuGK3OWdGWyHB-PRNuj8HpNLtL-GTcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love PK Cafe’!!! The service is excellent, super friendly staff. Their breakfast menu is almost like desserts, especially waffles and French toasts are unbelievable delicious, moist and crispy at the same time! I love my chicken lemongrass, so tender and flavourful. We can’t wait to try all of their dishes. To add to how wonderful this place is…the price is so affordable!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfrFZiCKbIhIzaUyEMRXaImFdwP6Ap1U7eiGgh&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-4-8"},{"Name":"Deborah H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsXwwC3s9WyQKJ7Zs95PXuhLbAGHn9sk0S1KGXgVkYpWzFwg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a nice surprise to find this great brunch place! Situated in an unassuming small neighbourhood plaza, PKs Cafe is a very clean cafe with a perfect selection of choices on the menu. We have been here a few times and it is always topnotch and tasty whether its breakfast or burgers. Their breakfast potatoes wedges and fries are just the right crispiness. Coming back to try their sandwiches next! Service is always friendly and love the attentive coffee refills.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP30Phpcy40cKMXuRkCo3k4xseN5ZBjAvd2aWS7&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2023-11-18"},{"Name":"Dariia Druzkina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1HtrODnJhuv0fWVXjF7xNuGcR7qBMJc7wC52gLfs1dI0JGA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It is a very cute cafe with big portions and amazing staff. The food was delicious and the menu has great options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3kHOFd3zoIPRpic-fVDR1pTnhEO9xOU7hJ5GR&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"Nick Tang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQkP22OPLsbOln7vAD-ae1LRI9zUvNKoMyd5lAIDRgo7JO2KRe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"HOLY!!! The Smoked Duck Benny was deliciously savoury without compromising too salty/saucy! The lemon truffle had a  crunchy exterior and seasoned perfectly. I ate it so fast that I forgot to take a pic!

The Banana Almond French toast was soooo soft, light and not overly sweet. Most places miss the mark by making them way too sweet (sickening even), but this place made what I can only describe as a fluffy cloud ☁️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMT2ii7umzJELBTgDbzMF4sQHmn-zKGU2LMv4hU&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-3-9"},{"Name":"Jimmy Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmaQe2WLp7herqsSS6Qbb3TdkPTjO2rKeO4tgMEL6Gag0kIT7k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sensational breakfast. They served great food with flexible options. The meal was filling. They had adequate condiments. They also make delicious soup. The food is cooked perfectly, therefore, it was a flawless execution. It’s definitely worth its rating, and I would highly recommend eating here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfMUQfP_csOgdrXJr2gBcHppoITpsoZIHVL0fd&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2023-7-30"}]

[{"Name":"Linh L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaB8qs_ygwwwpHNel9QXMXCKqxjoIZrWCW5N9kOTA3MUsIG0QWTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food quality has gone down quite a bit.  The service is still great and it's a clean place to dine at along with being able to accomodate larger tables.  I'd go again if it was the only option around here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVoOVfsz2IkZP8A7vFifm5tHHJIQd8T21GOmwQ&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"HW C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUg-IQKwQu37rrt2uXrxPur2eFHVtEh0sof-QwsldNZaEygI2hK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Been here twice, never again! Would have selected zero stars for food if that option was available. This isn't all the food we got. We also had a kid's meal and a onion soup. Super salty soup. Kid's meal was ok but pricey.
Basically everything in here is pricey yet quality is not up to par. Not an ordinary Hong Kong style cafe. Stay away!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJAxe1MU5inKBYv7ViYQ-mxrXjCf2k4WieUwed&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"TERRY CHENG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsg-oI6sco7O5Go48_oGM2GdPS9ywAc_QfXDXDKM3uhrlF3VpMxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food is delicious. I had the chicken with salted fish fried rice. It was made perfectly with wok hay. You can taste the salted fish. The kitchen forgot my wife's order but unlike other typical Asian restaurant where the server just says it is coming, she apologized and went to follow up immediately. The atmosphere is loud and tables cramped. It is busy so you definitely need to wait. The washroom is 3/5 stars. Difficult to find any slippery floor.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcw9bZT9QydmEGTIcGIKCSRHagLaVgqiZt-4Ml&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Kevin S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW-HoTH05SDyiEsT9u8Wd25Wyn-omXApiCGy1l-mOBxv_wj5xh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A fine Hong Kong style restaurant.

I found the prices a bit on the higher side, but just slightly. The portions were generous, and the baked rice was quite creamy and delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnMqJR3qWP9PZWzBIUrCkSJrm8aqc7e1v_rq0_&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Kanako Sakurada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYybgPjG_d3LYq66Ui47Ocd_2PMrfkKaju5V_L0IyVTR19lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"HK style cafe with wide variety of food from western to asian to fusion! Great steak combo and 10% off ordering on line even when eating in. Food is more than decent and the portion size is large.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNN16kz7Zh95HdWI--Ik0AAwQ2Z7ETsd_sBB0GP&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious and solid place for classic Hong Kong Cafe food. You can order online from your phone and they give you a 10% off discount if you order this way. There are plenty of combos that come with a drink and the menu is vast with both Western and Asian dishes. Highly recommend the tomato sauce baked ox tongue with a pasta of your choice. The tomato sauce was creamy, sweet, tangy, and savoury reminiscent of Campbell’s tomato soup. The lobster bisque was filled with lobster shell flavour. The red bean and grass jelly ice tasted delicious and refreshing serving as a dessert and drink at the same time.  Everything tasted delicious.

The portions for the fish and chips and pork and chicken cutlet and steak were good. There are comfy diner booth like seats to sit in and eat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOrZgPDR6-6MMRH7dQMHRUTXL89zevjiNTvoji&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2023-11-5"},{"Name":"Linda Vu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4Mt-fIM1ZKQuO_Y2ib9yo6xFV3B1mBRBjrbB_M80tp5QNaP0e=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best HK style cafe in Coquitlam.

Services and food are fast and efficient. The food is high quality and decently priced.

Breakfast ranges from $12-$14
Lunch ranges from $14-$18
Dinner set menus ranges from $19-$23","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0PCRS9s3F_2r1xDSLsmEsNMEbJdi19UCaeY6C&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-1-29"},{"Name":"ladan ghafouri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQKWEx_YV_Uj80v-xctgsLSGRY6V78hw5KMb4aNvRdZAaXJWti=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My partner and I went there for brunch.We ordered Mexican and vegetarian omelet. We pick the French toast to come with. Also we asked for coffee. The menu was really rich and you will have variety of different opinions. We really loved the omelets. The French toast was perfect.  For the coffee I just prefer to have suger, milk and cream on the table like as every where else( they just asked us how many suger we want and put 4 milk on the table, not even in the plate). Overall I really liked it and we will go back to try lunch and dinner .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHNXWlB85awZcVo4LsFWw7YzcOUxmmYs4aAxUG&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-4-8"}]
