[{"Name":"Madison G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtZsEld-Yz5a2Swm5LesjF83lo03ZXPGgujeQvQiLn6WLaIuGx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have lived here all my life and I never knew this place existed. Such a cute little restaurant right next to the docks. Food tasted amazing, the waitress was sooooo sweet and kind. Everyone sitting in there seemed as if they were at home. Seems like they were building a deck outside which will be nice to sit at in the summer. Will 100% be going back with my friends and family. Pricing is good, food is amazing, and staff is wonderful!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNr1jQTig5rZ535apc5yfpRhJajSDfVNHFj8qns&fid=0x0:0xa11864497c8bc2c0"],"When":"2021-3-7"},{"Name":"Evangeline Dalaya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVh6HgPE8PXFXtsvmH2vvn1nsy3lNWAduhT_pNqcs2QaQGPNZ6E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stumbled upon this place in yelp and gave it a try today. I loved the pirate theme of the restaurant. There are beautiful vines inside that are well taken care of. The owner Tammy is very friendly and this place has colouring books for children. The food was great! I'll be back again, thanks!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO73LYIufB83Yz_Gwy16iL1nF6f8wKoR1e-rBrx&fid=0x0:0xa11864497c8bc2c0"],"When":"2019-11-19"},{"Name":"Shray Khanna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxNTa-nYQS-Pu8SlxzhJqa4sQ-Kg1uVshYaqhJp-QUynRfCr0pbg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went there after a hike and this felt heavenly. It was the perfect breakfast place with lake on the side and a great service. The food was delicious and the staff were very friendly. It turns out to be my regular breakfast place after the hike. Would definitely recommend for everything especially the breakfast.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9Yvi9nl3ckRX-6U1i36V50DsMbKjCJ6uFzax4&fid=0x0:0xa11864497c8bc2c0"],"When":"2018-11-17"},{"Name":"Russell Toopitson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzZTFazrfUDRzOfCAmXm_e0kwjYMt5ikeVrrerf-k3NZRtoCaZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came for breakfest this morning with my friends, really nice view of the ocean and all the boats, all outdoor seating, owner was super friendly, our service was kinda slow new server girl seemed little confused, the food was amazing! all done perfectly. Quiet relaxing place for sunday breakfast. Recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWorQEjEFXjaC64GY75pgTjsx_cJRaYGRiAtlo&fid=0x0:0xa11864497c8bc2c0"],"When":"2021-5-2"},{"Name":"Cherry Cheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWe5x5A7FaU60jPX0fjGR_zbJxh8V7eH6ehlPyILwIl96V9M7_xWw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food at good prices! Very friendly staff. The yam fries were especially amazing. Dog friendly patio, and they brought out iced water for our pup! A little bit of a wait for food, but not too long, and food was super fresh. You don't need to pay for parking if you're eating there - Get a little parking pass from them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ellen Sea","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgyvw39gUnCgl6xsGC3h38EgAvDpICnxUdU619L8I4-wyV0VMy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here with my boyfriend for some brunch! I had the fish and chips and my boyfriend had the king willy burger. Right away, we noticed the warm hospitality. Service here is amazing, which is why I can see that this place is quite popular albeit a hidden gem. The prices are not bad too, on the cheaper side I'd say! This is the first time we've dined outside since the restrictions and it was a pleasant experience :). If I had one small critique, the burger patty itself sort of just seemed like someone cut out a round shape straight out of a ground beef package and then put it on the grill. You know when you get a ground beef package, the meat is squiggly. You could see the squiggly meat shape in the patty when it was served to us, which indicates that the patty itself probably wasn't seasoned. The burger still tasted good! But the look of the patty wasn't very pleasant. I would still very much recommend this place though. Very clean too!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cata Hana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIToB-HDjmqPgWwpB3oaJYkeKm9OXiQGiLpYJMPXLFMI1PGug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely, homey place with warm and welcoming staff.  :)  Had our staff party here and Kathy and Tammy served up yummy appies, drinks and were so kind to every member of our party.  We love it here!  :D We were thrilled to support a local eatery that offers such great food.  Often come for brunch too and it is always excellent! :D  I can't recommend this place enough! :D","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Freeze","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0SImYLtRlppzQUMpqpJ-E6EeYJ84ftn1mIcijt-QUiBdzYPM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I looked up brunch in Google, and Willy's came up in the top 3. The wife and I decided to check it out. We were very pleased with our visit. We were greeted like guest and not customers. I introduced Willy's to my brother, and he fell in love just as fast as we did. He now takes his daughters there as they fell in love with the place. We had the pleasure of all 5 of us having a great brunch together today. Staff as per norm were fun and warm. Just like an extension of family.

Great food, and Awesome staff. Very cozy place.
Thanks to all staff for the fun and food. See you soon.
John & Linda","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We finally discovered the best KBBQ in Coquitlam at Galbi! After trying several spots, this is the only place that truly got my partner excited about KBBQ. What sets Galbi apart is their focus on the quality of the meat rather than just the side dishes—a huge plus in our book.

They handled our reservation quickly, and we were fortunate to snag a table before it got really busy. While the space is a bit cozy, the meal was absolutely fantastic. The marinated beef short ribs were so irresistible that we ended up ordering extra.

We were expecting the bill to be around $200, but were pleasantly surprised when it came out $60 cheaper—even with the tip included. I’m definitely bringing my friends here next time. Can’t wait to come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtXU7g1Mdshu7JLv6kgKpUYZu5LSk1yfwe--bA&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Suzanne Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVA92S6YKukSMnbRa5H7tG8jeNNTYeIVRPnSfmNiCXXXyAauEzN0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came here on a Thursday evening and thankfully we came early! The place filled up pretty quickly around 7pm. We ordered the fresh beef ribs, pork jowl, and pork belly with skin on (thick cut). Prices are reasonable for the quality of meat and quantity (each portion is by weight). I found the soybean paste soup very salty, but once diluted it was quite tasty! Enjoyed the salad and sides, but they charge for extra side dishes and restrict you to 3 pieces of romaine lettuce per meat order (which seems a bit stingy for a small side item). There was also dirt on the lettuce, which they washed off and returned to us... Rice is ordered on the side for $2 each.

Overall a clean storefront with friendly staff, fresh quality ingredients, and a fun no-frills kbbq experience! We spent around $100 for 3 people.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMolYBIiES1jj5IW8KrAnPCgFR-qT5oYoTiMa20&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2023-11-3"},{"Name":"MAY 매이 Elford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxJVIiA7BVVmzUGqT6sRzP7-hCdYJttIOnYMeIvWOWZPmq7cr7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A Saturday evening out with my friends. 4 of us ended up at Galbi. We ordered the pork belly with skin on, Galbi, and the cold noodle. Everything was delicious… the bean paste soup was so yummy.
They gave us side dishes, but to add more, there is an extra fee.
Service was great and there have a lot of parking. Definitely worth going!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiNt4K-oH50HrFkg3LuUdGSxwY6y2kJMYXzNyD&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2023-4-28"},{"Name":"Ananda Enkhtur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkkmVVa6j0bCuttopPInRikVrpr7LXYSHoZtWk3dhng__J_lZi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tried this place the other day and it was pretty good! Not many items on the menu that you can choose from but overall the taste was delicious. Especially the red bean soup and the corn cheese was so good. Like many Korean restaurants there are variety of side dishes that come with the meal and the portions for each one was generous too! Would recommend to come as a big group tho!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ-sZtMzSf8pafLObOPwMYuYYoPalr6VIO6Vud&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2024-2-20"},{"Name":"Nat A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnjKr4KNFAObzj2bIvH9BRInxwKsSvEg1PM25bKfvhxtWZTWHoog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Tried this place out for the first time. We had the marinated beef and pork short ribs. The beef was tasty but the pork was just okay. I had a few pieces of the beef that were hard and fatty. The portion size for the meat was average. The soup appetizer, kimchi, and pickled raddish were good. They provided a pitcher of water, no complimentary tea offered.

The selection on the menu is minimal.

Service was average. We had to wave over to the waiters every time we needed something. They did not come up to us and ask how things were after they gave us our food.

Overall, the food was decent but I wouldn't come back when there are other Korean BBQ restaurants with more selection.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPb8x1RQYXa6xENsHZCT5yvKAqEx9VI05wYGrBK&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2022-12-11"},{"Name":"Molly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxkBBeHfwDYZEHKteGzubNOwVdGJVg2Kn4pysUcR2QBA2w0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jessi was my server tonight she was very friendly and attentive. 5 stars for my experience. Food was great. The free soup was so good I purchased another one! They didn't seem to have the salt soya sauce dip tray that you get in other places. Maybe you have to ask for it? I don't care for it I don't add extra stuff to my meat. I got the short ribs and the prime beef so good!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVumoVlQ2Nr7knqW9lb01ghVZite-FLKkjhE2dVSofQsuYeSfVW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Galbi is my best place for Korean BBQ in Vancouver. The meats were fresh, tender and nicely marbled also marinated short ribs were well seasoned. Excellent service and reasonable price. I usually visit 1-2times a week. Try this place if you are meat lover!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4RXzzsu5isoPwissTXgbEx26fjigui8uk6uai&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2023-2-28"},{"Name":"Hwa D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwQyjGi41SNIX6tVkw-8BfQdSHpbL_wDTFcZShwlM2dHZ3e1AW_w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited this restaurant and was thoroughly impressed. The marinated beef short ribs were absolutely delicious.
What made the experience even more enjoyable was the exceptional service. The staff were incredibly friendly and attentive, ensuring that our dining experience was delightful from start to finish. I highly recommend this restaurant","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOklX-zzm88iNsKQfia31-tC_DHWRFqVfVdVqKY&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2024-3-17"}]

It's such a beautiful place where you can enjoy a stroll by the lake or hang out with friends and family. You can even go paddling! I highly recommend trying the Rocky Point ice creams. I tried the yogurt cookie one, and it made my day better! Thank you, team, for the great job!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmmOSrt6TT8TQlzZM3NBk9GQWiYGVCAm7ay6n7&fid=0x0:0x9a8bc29c45c901ac"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Sathiyaseelan Suhashini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGCDhZwAvUF3Q8iMEpEx8TQCvKbwiXzYFJN0uOrenEt7v0wxGX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome flavours and taste. A must try 😊

We tried hokey pokey, double chocolate with raspberries, rum raisin. Delicious treat.

Single scoop with cone is around $ 6.5. Just a scoop in a cup is $ 5.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAaZyJYTEF7CZ8SEoDqPuILp812rolIkAVrvVF&fid=0x0:0x9a8bc29c45c901ac"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Jessy J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHNRFw0Z_JgaU0TxGr1Pv5X-w9V6JzR0bnCuTDlGr_7pfsbx_k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a beautiful treat for a park visit. Just plan your time as there’s usually a line up. But have to say the line does move rather quickly.

We tried mint chocolate chip and cotton candy it was delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcPyuE3capNqmi9XknrYa-BlIBBLTBPRUYp_wn&fid=0x0:0x9a8bc29c45c901ac"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Daniel Silver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJawI80c4qwvuA-pWmht_nhIypwFKNS8vUDHnZIepoqs0gJvft7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Lots of flavors and in a good location to attract people. I liked how they posted the flavours outside so you could see the options before lining up inside. Personally I found the ice cream okay but not something I'd go back for. Kids will enjoy it though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMx_gukWuEomTjSZtGejH8icSlRLvUL8ze0Iy9X&fid=0x0:0x9a8bc29c45c901ac"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"S Kaushal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwZIWG8PGNb9zPTo2E5Ikortc_CRZ7cLPTXU0S_q0sxazY8g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Excellent Ice creams. At my age chocolate love is over.

Mint is the in thing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN82TNdLsnYbONqeUUdiDPQTorLOcgTFcbyusUq&fid=0x0:0x9a8bc29c45c901ac"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The summer lineup is an indication of how good this locally-produced ice cream is. We love the variety of flavours and cones. When family comes to visit, we go for an after dinner walk to get ice cream and stroll through the park. One of the many reasons Port Moody is a great location in metro Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3NjJAzpMEZXhSmYgqgBvsrhxAYP3Vog47WtNf&fid=0x0:0x9a8bc29c45c901ac"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So many flavours of ice cream to choose from, it can be overwhelming. Love the Rocky Point Ice Cream by Rocky Point Park. It’s open year round and it’s a great little shop to get a sweet treat for yourself once in a while. Other than ice cream by the scoop, they also sell ice cream cakes, pints of ice cream, and clothing merchandise. Employees are efficient at their jobs and can clear the customer line pretty quickly. Lots of parking nearby at the free lot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgPCTyRDOfdidP5HZ-7SkN5ZPgTQHIkBNEd6SF&fid=0x0:0x9a8bc29c45c901ac"],"When":"2024-1-8"},{"Name":"W P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQlM7TSl65Iw3PbziChxkjB8ZQft91ZSv7cXHl8cFmHfamUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"They don't have spoons, just tiny wooden paddles that are impossible to eat ice cream with and taste like wood. Terrible, just cause you can't serve single use plastics doesn't mean there's no good alternatives besides a shitty wooden stick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPr4_JVGmz7OSfzRn7WUZc6yiIrjaYLvwaS9Mb8&fid=0x0:0x9a8bc29c45c901ac"],"When":"2024-11-26"}]

[{"Name":"Andy Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWooGSzw1FKhky_mrftz_qLp6fsBzAqJ7JcjT2pde1tUMh4Y9hx8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Shrinkflation and inflation.

Dishes taste fine but the prices are going up and the portion seems shrinking as well.
I ordered to pick up some dishes. $6.25 for 6 pieces of small spicy salmon roles.
Maybe I’m out of touch these days. $32.25 for takeouts does not go very far these days I guess.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHN74PVQXn88pZBDO_WRQkASFUILQKLltLDqPH&fid=0x0:0xd5be1ea94eed26b2"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Mohammad Tabesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjokXICqa-0DdrHKHh0Wt3GGaHTAC4RDuOqk22M3flRzjmqoKo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good quality food for the price with a nice variety, really quick service and convenient location inside the mall. It's a budget place with disposable plates and chopsticks. Miso soup was plain but tasty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPL_iRBW2adsUvuZctF90SuqpluYd65jND4m7dv&fid=0x0:0xd5be1ea94eed26b2"],"When":"2024-9-14"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My partner works in the mall and grabs lunch here three times a week, especially loving the teriyaki. I had the chance to try the unagi oshi sushi, and it was delicious! The creamy prawn tempura was a fantastic bonus, making the meal even more delightful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6on5Y08KZ9VAGnb-Q10oavACH62ly3bxzrkNn&fid=0x0:0xd5be1ea94eed26b2"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Armin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVKfPvn-jqW8hTOlU1VeElw6vFvjre9PTWSba_96soEJn4hAFVjA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good Sushi for being in the mall! Lots of options to pick and you can order online so you don't have to wait!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5ux3twBDePDGec0k-4hwPkab1Rd92kFjUs18y&fid=0x0:0xd5be1ea94eed26b2"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"I D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJePVcTLvMpAzx-nv1Jiy6G3BSAT8AXC96M8bp3iDt95AnsQw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I wish Coquitlam Centre has better eateries. I ordered the Beef Bento. Price was okay, but the portions were not big. For $15, I only got 4 pieces of California roll instead the standard 6 pieces. I was surprised by the quantity of the beef. It was more than I expected but the beef quality was quite poor. There was also not a lot of rice. Salad was fresh. Service was quick and friendly. It's a small place, and I couldn't find a place to sit, so I had the food to go. I forgot to ask for napkins :(","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexis Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4lll3FSw4DuoAXTTSQfNVd2BMOvLsNf0gg2O5LBY3etPVgQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the prawn tempura and miso soup. For mall sushi, this place is consistently great! I enjoy eating here and will always return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEOr8Ou4QsT2tC4bIAmYmBwtpMCrNDvv-oKLq1&fid=0x0:0xd5be1ea94eed26b2"],"When":"2024-1-14"},{"Name":"K S H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUpfuZFJ8RwqNTmsEi_Ve_L99RruCBycZdik5Nf-7YZZhK-hRF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the Best Sushi places in Coquitlam and very conveniently located in the mall.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtjlH9F0FcLxhh45QyYB26pLJ8aF_QRpWZxyIU&fid=0x0:0xd5be1ea94eed26b2"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Johnny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvkqlZ5wz-o7qQiMAPvxq4Uq26umX4_opBke6CDrVfkbGhCeuLaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My first time at Togo Sushi was excellent. With exceptional service by the lady employee, I ordered the teriyaki bento box, and I opted for chicken rather than beef. The teriyaki bento box comes with California rolls, salad, gyoza, and miso soup. The teriyaki chicken was, to be honest, disappointing, which I was not expecting. I also ordered yam rolls, which I loved since I love sweet potatoes. Would I go back? Likely not.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Meghan Atkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpn_HJKLz67oWun2TqZ53LpPOuwDcgytLe9I7rJRW9gkR5zUDI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered take out tonight from Dinakis (through skip the dishes). Ordered my regular Greek dish, the chicken souvlaki. I often order from another restaurant but thought I would give Dinakis a try. Upon eating my chicken souvlaki skewer, I noticed the taste and texture of the chicken seemed off. To my surprise the chicken was raw in the middle. The restaurant was immediately called to inform them. They stated that we needed to contact skip for a refund (which is fine!) and said the chicken was raw due to how busy the restaurant was tonight. Unfortunately, I do not see this as a valid reason for serving undercooked meat. They offered to remake the meal and have me come and pick it up. Unfortunately with a baby in bed, leaving the house is not option which is why I ordered in.

I’ll no longer be order from Dinakis. Perhaps if the situation had been dealt with differently on their end I would. However, it’s all left a bad taste in my mouth - no pun intended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPamzWqtMSJD_2lXqeftQ04VTeQ-qet20_AUo7c&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Queenie Chao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZJZmSpZQRAFF9t6SoJ29KP7hdKen-l5gR8pgpgRf7-1s6aED9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here for my dad's birthday. Service was excellent! Food was great - the roast lamb, chicken marsala, and moussaka were all amazing, especially the lamb! The only exception was the steak, which was over cooked and full of gristle. To make up for it, they offered us a tiramisu cake which worked out well and was tasty too. Would definitely come back for the lamb and try other items too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUkbQOcVFipathRk-dHPJeXSBTX5g93Ke5HcNA&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Jessica Tite","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDIMc556UvdeCdK2q0SIDelAc_HJzjyapBYqP0A0CPBdyeWUex=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best Mediterranean food I've had! It's no wonder they have so many awards/accolades at the entrance way.
The food is incredible: well priced, fresh and great portions.
The restaurant is neat and clean, including the washrooms. It has a very cozy feel inside.
Service was excellent!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2zKnmJCNiyvvJJiFSndVY5qI8Go-Dp0HU1Vdj&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2024-2-11"},{"Name":"Al So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLumQHIv-5W9wXPr4ZbA1zWCVnPk2w1Kc3bjsO93-VMG-v7JQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re in the Shaughnessy area in Poco and craving some Mediterranean magic, look no further than Dinakis Mediterranean Grill. Let me just say, the portions here are generously sized, so come prepared to feast!

The tzatziki is a standout—nice and fresh, with a flavor that’ll make your taste buds do a happy dance. It's the perfect companion to their delicious offerings.

Speaking of which, the Souvlaki Combo is a real treat. It comes with beef, chicken, and prawn souvlaki, each one cooked to perfection. The beef is tender, the chicken is juicy, and the prawns are succulent. It's a delightful trio that hits all the right notes.

We also tried the roast lamb, which was cooked to perfection. It wasn't fatty, and the meat just came off the bone. We thoroughly enjoyed it.

For those dining with little ones, you'll be pleased to know they offer kids' portions. These come with one skewer instead of two at a reduced price, making it great value. It’s the perfect way to keep the kids happy without breaking the bank.

Overall, Dinakis Mediterranean Grill is a great spot for hearty portions, fresh flavors, and good value. Make sure to bring your appetite—you won’t be disappointed!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNi-Vmmgslvmp-CsAb30_lQnluDK_dEqTU341G1&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"Patrick Laplante","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEQ6rmzYgqU18BgeUeFbN3j9UzTXOfNOAqOLvy-TwFRIxBth-Q7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Firstly, the service and the staff are absolutely fantastic. Secondly, the food quality is great, it's really great value, huge portions, and always fresh. And thirdly, great drink selection, and I was happy to hear that they can accommodate large parties as well. Whether for a cute date, family dinner, birthday celebration or quick lunch, I'd highly recommend!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGEpDRCp2o6wFFn9ZB0lPz_oE8b1ckSu6JjaQG&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2024-1-8"},{"Name":"Julian Sara Joseph","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWofxVvuCZOl3BWxzMUTJPVosg-yW0WoAuPTsW6aFO5_K2yZycmSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Greek food here was truly authentic and tasty. Souvlaki of all varieties was great. We had come back from a trek and all our tiredness was gone with the kind servers and their affordable but yummy food ❤️their portion sizes are quite large so it is filing. Loved the presentation too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJvrpsBh0Cgol4Hr9mDBGY6_JEDFnb7KJHbIEJ&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2023-4-4"},{"Name":"Cheryl G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQZ5krFYmB32nSSVZRn_5-zzzmWzMyLr7fQFLOSOH_4NttzFie=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Overall good experience. We had regular entrees but also ordered happy hour appetizers, portions was a little small. I also found that an automatic 18% gratituity was surprising for 7 people dining. But we enjoyed the food with our dining guests and I would recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thom Slater","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNyquzT0Ty5ga2cGbYXqVQ4Zp1mr8dSG4EejGqH4R5Eqad_PSB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in for an extended family dinner. Really generous portion sizes, the lamp chops were fantastic.
Other than the great food, what really made this a 5 star experience was the incredible service from Mariah.
She took our 12 person reservation last minute despite being solo, had such great energy the whole night, and really made it an enjoyable time for everyone. We'd come back just for her.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Daizy Ferigotti","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUx-eE9w0IbqKKwK_c6P5QKvrY9JYmNmQ2XnpYRPWBbV_jOMCAeOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered the brownie cake with brigadeiros and grape surprise for my employee's birthday. We usually have a coffee break at the office, and I introduced the Brazilian birthday sweets to my team. Everything was absolutely delicious! Everyone loved it, especially the grape surprise—it was such a unique and creative touch. The flavor, portions, and presentation were all flawless.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMqDXeUtVUeZnQezKBc9Bbo8aPJ4HD3HnAmFkK&fid=0x0:0x771c183d8b741593"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Chloe P.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOd_k819TESfS_1UYIzyA7DvAbrwpJ3dshJgc2zLqPvpO9BA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolute amazing experience ordering from Maria, with a beautiful end result.

After reading all the glowing reviews, I purchased an orange cake for my mum’s birthday, citrus being her favourite desert base. The orange flavour was perfectly balanced and delicate, and it was soooo moist.

We ordered a small, and their are easily 10 healthy portions. The purchasing process was easy, and pickup was a breeze.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOa5hQsVs-MZl3ISxyYVqmvQzWyer40GeHsGXDK&fid=0x0:0x771c183d8b741593"],"When":"2021-3-7"},{"Name":"Trevor Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW9xnNvBIaKPG4BLBovxEtWuFtEITtD24XVqm5AvwQ0R4L-kgU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredible! I ordered the Brownie Cake for my wife's Birthday. Amazing! My son has requested it for his Birthday. I don't know if I can wait till April. Lol","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFiHoGU4to0skjY25el4CK3J7M0g11zs8tZKviGpDfccasPwo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Doceria da Maria is absolutely wonderful. I was in a pinch and needed a cake for work celebration. I contacted Maria on Sunday, needing the cake for Monday, and she had it done in just a few hours. She was more than willing to work around my schedule and do whatever she could to make it work for her customer. I ended up going with the orange cake at her recommendation, and it was such a hit. It was so beautifully decorated (picture), and my god it was delicious!! Everyone loved it, and wanted to know where I'd gotten it. We were all very impressed.

Thank you Maria! I will be ordering the Doce da Leite next time, thanks to that delicious sample you included. 15/10 would recommend your business to everyone :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqie8n7tfVxEm7JBshVQZmnLhWv9a9cl-OU9Y&fid=0x0:0x771c183d8b741593"],"When":"2017-6-13"},{"Name":"ridvan t","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFnmnYRhSVOj1LDdhErDnSsnxlF_5_XoPsFmpvGmOgUuHP2g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First of all, this is a pre-order business. If you want a cake done, you call ahead and request what you want. However, on a last minute call I made to her, I was lucky that she had one of her orange cake in hand. I personally not a big fan of zesty cakes but this one was really good. Not overwhelmingly orangey, nor too sweet. The cake was really soft. My wife really liked it. We will definitely consider ordering from here in the future","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHzowIJwYfheNGdIk5wKLr95ZLe-gcFZrs0x6H&fid=0x0:0x771c183d8b741593"],"When":"2018-4-14"},{"Name":"Jestina Simpson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWenjuVlPeNFQBzK_LD_Ty21HbjsrKLujfNFQkOs7SJGfwhYRvdOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered the gluten-free brownie pie and orange cake for a birthday party.  The birthday boy has gluten allergy and we must say both were delicious. Our friends and family also gave us great feedback too and they couldn't even tell the cakes were gluten free.  Maria was very responsive to the orders and very nice to interact with.

We will definitely be ordering cakes from her...and will have to try out each different type of cakes she offers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jiyeon You","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJdjuGDGM2HBwNdTb6cOMhnbX41furDzkRoHTsg40s2L2q3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered an orange cake with raspberry the day before my husband's birthday and received it the next day. I'm really appreciated for her prompt action. The cake was so beautifully decorated. It wasn't too sweet and it's like a real homemade cake. We were all satisfied with the cake even my little daughter! It was absolutely delicious and perfect with coffee. I'm highly recommend orange cake. I will definitely order it again! :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Peggi Peacock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLt8odVjMpEWudwHlhg-x6EvxM34saOOqNtqdvAdy4ZZ8ISXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered a key lime pie for my southern husband's birthday. Had to order on short notice and needed something nut safe. Doceria da Maria were able to not only make a fabulous pie but did it over night and made it totally nut safe! We'll be ordering lots from here from now on. Thanks so much. Highly recommend these wonderful women!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Dana Sullivan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQIw-0oOUNgoyniYugTscGkgpKJS8tpx4V0tAajn3ZGkNIfqEk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really nice aesthetic at this coffee shop, which is situated alongside a presentation centre and also features a small pop-up shop from Fable (housewares). The layout is very open but still features a good amount of comfortable seating including seating for large groups, and a beautiful patio out back. The service was friendly.
I had a blackberry & brie grilled cheese, a vegan rye cookie, and a tropical espresso spritz (seasonal drink, like an espresso tonic with coconut and pineapple flavours). Everything was really good! I love fruit with brie cheese so the grilled cheese was an easy winner for me. The blackberry spread was tart and jammy which balanced out the rich brie cheese. I loved the funky flavour of rye in the cookie and the chewiness. The espresso spritz was very refreshing in this hot weather! It had deflated a little by the time I took the picture, but it had an impressively foamy crema layer. Even though nothing was really fancy or experimental, all the food/drink items I tried had something to make them a little unique.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCEBQuCDIsCUWtrbHKFNiwZ3ZKq7ylWlDlHn48&fid=0x0:0x775eee3d482be6bc"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Vicente Barreiros","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXXjeDynmf81Pwbj0gtZnbrkTAQXze5uhpr2fBUeDvR8QxnMvZfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely fantastic experience at The Outpost Café in Coquitlam! From the moment we walked in, we were greeted with friendly smiles and a warm atmosphere. The coffee was exceptional, rich and flavorful, and the pastries were fresh and delicious. The menu offers a great variety, with something for everyone, including vegan options. The service was prompt and attentive, making us feel right at home. The cozy decor and comfortable seating made it the perfect spot to relax, play some cards, and enjoy our meal. Highly recommend The Outpost Café for anyone looking for a top-notch café experience. Five stars all the way!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4wvHezthRzyRsko09vUr_HYZOtSR2BH7Mwg61&fid=0x0:0x775eee3d482be6bc"],"When":"2024-7-5"},{"Name":"Penny Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCDgTL2OCcG7L7sb4kqDmHWrJHfxt_0ygdBvV9n-aV-_JDvgc9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place to have a cute cafe moment.
The coffee was great, the breakfast was good.
Great seating area, friendly staff and everything fits a relaxing work from cafe vibe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcO0eFIZ_w7h0KLt86R7SxjHYM-KQnPOHfMhxM&fid=0x0:0x775eee3d482be6bc"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"First time here. We both found the espresso acidic, and my latte was watery, so not an enjoyable combination. $15 avocado toast got us a cold hard boiled egg on a slice of bread. Bizarrely there was dill in it which wasn’t nice. It was as if AI was asked to create a recipe for avocado toast and this was the result. Service was basic and gets three stars. Atmosphere was the best part and gets five stars.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwTG5Fyw5A_PZTIuU9hJ9zw5QI8f6DPjm6FLG5&fid=0x0:0x775eee3d482be6bc"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"Mahsa Haghjoo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRSnT0Wip7Pbg6Z8m0cglGHkWd61YfkTkUIlG6b0IkPWIUcJi2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a lovely clean place with indoor and outdoor sitting area. Absolutely delicious matcha tea latte and almond croissant ( super crisp and not too sweet).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3AZ75H1zqQhXLwfTg9Rv_YKW4qW3nOf8lfejs&fid=0x0:0x775eee3d482be6bc"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"candy L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgq2OgnXFRsC1icGye-CTgUf_6kEV0cPoOgzI7ANMes5eDT-Xz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Today I  visited this coffee shop that was recommended by a friend, and I was impressed by the uniqueness of both the interior and exterior design. The outdoor seating area was adorned with lights and some seats even had heaters above them. The indoor area also had a distinct and interesting design.
I ordered a mocha and a Cosmic Candy espresso, and only saw two types of pastries  available at the counter, so I chose  chocolate cookies. As we had our dog with us, we decided to sit outside. The mocha had a great taste, but the espresso wasn’t  my preferred flavor .. The chocolate cookie had a soft texture and a slightly salty taste, which I really enjoyed. I was glad I bought two pieces of it.

Overall, the experience was good, although the staff wasn't particularly friendly. [{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Conveniently located near the SkyTrain and Coquitlam Centre. The staff were super friendly, and the lobster dunk, ribs, and steak were absolutely delicious—highly recommended! The ambiance was cozy and inviting. Will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5lCB7UYXuKglJCHEcLCgizeN6zWPuTR_mKGf-&fid=0x0:0xa8c5636616493c53"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Parya Salehi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbh4w9SWNAXiJGP9wxzBZJLCCi91QA6ycLqmxcg8Loj48hcg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Tonight, I had the worst dining experience of my life. Due to power outages, we decided to have dinner at Mr. Mike’s, a place we’ve been to before. Unfortunately, tonight was absolutely horrible.

First, we placed our orders, and it took an unusually long time for the food to arrive. When it finally did, my plate was completely cold. The staff took it back to warm it up, but that was just the beginning.

I ordered a medium-rare steak, as I always do, but it came out rare. The meat was incredibly tough, making it almost impossible to cut and chew. On my first bite, I nearly choked and had to be helped by a nearby table. Shockingly, the manager didn’t seem to care about the situation at all. They simply removed the cost of the meal from the bill, without offering any real apology or concern.

I was left struggling to breathe, and the only comment the manager made was, “You ordered a medium-rare steak.” I always order medium-rare, and I know the difference between rare, medium-rare, and medium. This steak was not only rare but also so tough that it was hard to cut in the first place!

I am deeply disappointed with the lack of care or professionalism shown during this experience. I will definitely think twice before returning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pam Delfino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVou97WNj_X-lZ_I6WAUZr7ELzzqVVEd-LYy7ydp9dEDslErRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fun place to enjoy a tasty meal and some brews! Very friendly service! ❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2j1QY0G9zmTHxjbcYdSBuKt4DJPhlAhXMfv8Y&fid=0x0:0xa8c5636616493c53"],"When":"2024-10-29"},{"Name":"Haas Eskandanian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9IADx9YthZR1vOZb8_xNjKOZYe9q3dvXswpievCacAQi6Xm67=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I don’t know how this restaurant is still in business but I’m sure they will one of the next chains going out of business soon.
Ribeye steak was cold, chewy and very late on the table! Don’t waste your night and money here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvsQaKgpL9nNiQwP8NJZXjFXnjvxN3hLywRHA9&fid=0x0:0xa8c5636616493c53"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Fatemeh Mohammadnejad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_vxxy0DRS_-_0DEH_6td4t10kAYXF76jysJTuML9DO4CHIlU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My go to restaurant for any occasion! Great atmosphere, delicious food, and always a wonderful experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMciwfSqYoAS6jb1sLCwQDbHILVCq5VqSndNvfO&fid=0x0:0xa8c5636616493c53"],"When":"2024-11-1"},{"Name":"Richard Filgate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqY0CH1XgGWiOwrSaofbVKHTYfrBSo2qLPtYgxiWh2x5oOWqQp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today I had lunch at Mr Mike's steak house in Coquitlam bc
Order the classic Mr Mike Burger by mistake and even though it was just meat and cheese and bun it was quite delicious our waitress was polite and caring and would recommend eating here for lunch 👍👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzd8FS8nOKEA4BK9aYw7JL2wsCQzLe4hjBFH_c&fid=0x0:0xa8c5636616493c53"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"ZuffaLtdDanaWhite","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6gGe3NbbgwlJVAvgbTW4PyVUNZSvDx9TwIaijDSbPkD-WMrs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time to Mr. Mikes. Expectations going in was not what I experienced. If you’re in I suggest you try and order an 8oz striploin (medium rare) w/ chimichuri & the keto option. Salad was amazing in itself. Steak was on point! Soft and succulent & full of flavour. The waitress Cassidy was very attentive and came by our table 4x’s to check up and bring extra items. Very pleasant experience! Will definitely be returning.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUPThP2riuEei0GIGcgF645Nxz2_aVP7UHJ817&fid=0x0:0xa8c5636616493c53"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Denny Hui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuGFgsc9U61TCKDV21ZHXILH-aGrlI-hjZswBeAYg3LhKf97Y3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Went to Mr. Mike's after my sons soccer game last week. Restaurant is modern and spacious. Seats are comfortable.

Staff was friendly. Atmosphere was lively and welcoming.

Food on the other hand was ok. My son ordered the Sirloin and Lobster Mac. Sirloin was tough to cut and chew.  Lobster mac bland taste. Our burgers also bland.

I ordered the Nashville Hot Chicken sandwich. Flavour was good but chicken patty was very small.

Overall ok experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkhqoEFfTPptXrtv_oqjfXPOjpc-iRD4blLilS&fid=0x0:0xa8c5636616493c53"],"When":"2024-2-11"}]

While the walk from the Port Moody train station was somewhat unpleasant, we were glad to have found this place for lunch.  We ordered the Hamburger and Chicken Salad Sandwich, which came out quickly. The portion was large for the price and the food was tasty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONs_OUjS3AMVH_a3sq2K_FXyhtR64BjhC5sKGR&fid=0x0:0x4b0f999511d92c06"],"When":"2024-3-20"},{"Name":"Mike Tinsley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-mwqoDiqTTIYumo48rL4HdDTCYvHkpT-E5OKHgd7UsWfR6ho0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow! I can't believe I haven't been here before, what an amazing place. The food is absolutely delicious, the staff are friendly and the prices are unreal. I ate inside and the portions they gave were huge! The teriyaki beef sandwich was really good.

The next day I did a big takeout order for 12 people and we all really enjoyed it. We had to call a bit ahead but it was worth it.

If you're looking for a chill place to grab lunch, or just looking for a bagel on the run, I highly recommend this wonderful restaurant!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"PTTN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVXQhrf96EsaD027m51yX-Uvc0Kdpt5n8uGLLy_w4vgEoUTTPd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This establishment won awards for good reason. I could not find a fault in anything we experienced there. We went after they received that national award. It was busy and the anticipated wait time was over an hour and a half! We were greeted with warmth and patience. As if we were the only people there. We ordered a drink and had it on the patio as we waited for our table. Truth be told, the owner got us in in under half and hour so we were EXTREMELY lucky and grateful. Drinks were delicious. Food was phenomenal. I can't stress enough the attention to detail these people have for every portion of dinner service. Well done and well deserved! Keep it up!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqaM9dL5KXg_NjYfLhmt2xgQmSQG7gSLfz1pdv&fid=0x0:0x914dae93368664f4"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"William Ting","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVROj5tKGe8MbrrNOhk8-59eVUA_x7_lmH6eRP-mRZLTzD9H6iPlA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our group of 4 had 3 pizzas and 1 pasta. It was more than enough for us! Delicious Naples style pizza.

A variety of unique flavours that you would not get anywhere else. It worked out to be $30 per person.

An absolutely great deal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRnjle-60dbG3m6hECOokahqlC60-9Fo0TyW5d&fid=0x0:0x914dae93368664f4"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Jacob Gilbert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrUQKdbxQwz9AjjpsHYxJOv7HC_xp-KAOyVPcTzB05b6NESS0F=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely amazing experience! From the moment we walked in, we were warmly greeted at the door. Despite the restaurant being very busy (a testament to the incredible food), we were seated within 20 minutes at the pizza bar, which turned out to be such a treat. Watching the fire oven in action and seeing the pizzas being crafted added a whole new level of excitement to our visit.

We were served by the general manager, Vita, who was outstanding! She made us feel so welcome, almost like we were guests in her own home. Her warmth and attentiveness truly elevated the experience.

We ordered pizza, pasta, and truffle fries—all of which were phenomenal. Every bite was bursting with flavor, and it’s clear the quality of the food matches the hype.

Highly recommend this place to anyone looking for top-notch food and a great atmosphere. We’ll definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6fksMOtEGkiPkVmh_o_SVQGOJZ_x19PUAFUCQ&fid=0x0:0x914dae93368664f4"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Clara Chau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoMWRC0cDGP4nCpQ1_Zdm86daXS0A0KJbVAa9QczqqbfD7fWIZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here after seeing a lot of buzz on Instagram and it lived up to the hype! We came for lunch and I suggest coming right at opening to make sure you get a table on weekend without waiting for too long. The pizza was delicious and had generous toppings. What I liked about the pizza is how thin the crust is but at the same time, it's chewy on the inside with a nice crunch on the outside. Each pizza was the perfect size to cut into 4 slices for sharing and we ended up ordering 4 different pizzas to try. The gnocchi was baked beautifully but the combo of cheese was too much for me but the rest of the table loved it! We also ordered the truffle risotto croquettes and it was my favourite dish. The truffle wasn't overpowering and it was fried really well on the outside. We have plans to come back another time to try other pizzas.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMlkIWYpKBwpgHUbEb7lAPZzbum8KOcKcBnMlbv&fid=0x0:0x914dae93368664f4"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"Adriana Neradovicova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqZwq8WG9dS74sb6OU2T1ULrs1Txr0UHRpcfrPsiphWlDMuA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After a long year I came back with my friends to dine in your marvellous restaurant. My last experience was amazing! Your restaurant looks great, food is spectacular and service was sensational! Coincidentally we were lucky to have same waiter year ago as a last night. Left was very kind to us and his service was outstanding in both cases.
After having very good time last year my friend and I, we ask Left to make a picture with us. He kindly agreed.
So after recognizing him tonight I couldn’t hold back, so I mentioned the fact we already met and I presented the picture from that day. 😀 He immediately remembered us 😃 We didn’t hesitate and had to capture this moment again!!!
Left really made our night unforgettable again and I hope we’ll have more chances to come back for more memories like this. 🙏
Thank you","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNd8r46ixHQKMHdkvaEfagU1S8RoFgigHGEFP3b&fid=0x0:0x914dae93368664f4"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Ellen Shi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOAMbx6gFFkXfXX1M1IsnQtaa9zAErN_pvBjN5pKz7C9O5Nw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everything about my experience was excellent, from the delicious food to the outstanding service! I can confidently say this is the best pizza I've ever had. I’m already looking forward to returning to try other dishes from the menu!😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDM7X1P9NyS0Gf2ga-g0Aq-sqTbQxuLQ1q97cc&fid=0x0:0x914dae93368664f4"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Mohammadreza Behnejad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbfFjgusvHBDGevsLnSFlRH6CqkrxaSYgN1dtBgif3eqTdhnw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious dishes and staff are nice and professional
Great atmosphere and well designed inside
Traditional napoleon pizza are great specially comes with fresh mozzarella
Dough is fluffy and mouth watering

Pizza was a little over cooked and dough was burned

There are a couple of parking spots available and plenty of street parking

Highly recommend to do advance booking. Wait time over the weekend could be an hour easily","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNC7I4Czp97ghD76EJMNa45c5n0cB4Rpsjd-YA&fid=0x0:0x914dae93368664f4"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Shawn Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqLU-WOCdxBtbaD48HbqFqhf-gwdu5I-zJsKM-w1J0K1gsKg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food here was unbelievable! The aged prosciutto was to die for & the focaccia was crispy on the outside, but pillowy on the inside. The pizza was also excellent! Although the dough was a bit soft in the middle, the flavour made up for it. If it wasn’t for our server who took over 15 minutes to even greet us & was generally slow with service, I’d give this place 5 stars. Definitely add it to your “must try” list.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGV2m3LmvzeJxcP3UgDg70aEa8Nwio_cA9w3yx&fid=0x0:0x914dae93368664f4"],"When":"2024-12-2"}]

[{"Name":"Kimiya Namdar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5NoUG9m0kwHJtkvaDA-UHALghW-sRI1Mo4nWzPLFWn5wQUVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For our anniversary, we decided to stay local and chose Cactus Club, and it didn’t disappoint. We arrived 15 minutes early but were seated promptly. Moe, our host, was attentive and made sure we were well taken care of. We both ordered the steak, which was delicious and came in generous portions. When it came time to settle the bill, we were pleasantly surprised to find that our dessert was on the house—a thoughtful gesture for our special occasion. It’s the little touches like these that make all the difference.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlxtSajFGYkpR7ks7zBaxq3E_Rq1AoW205uJz3&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"jackie spears","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQSpIRsoeLZKzPhRjMQrTuHhWXI2eeJUv_G6fSe8jGwzpSrvc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Wish I could give no stars,but had to put something unfortunately.
So loud couldn't hear anything from my coworkers to the server. Food was cold and tasteless (had the chicken strips and truffle fries) fries weren't even seasoned and I paid extra $$$ for the upgrade only to have tasteless fries and cold chicken strips! Will not ever be returning to this location.
Also to add the Bellini I had was definitely definitely not worth the price I paid for either and had like no alcohol in it! Another major let down which is another staple CC is known for!
Have had mediocre service from this location before and now after this last service will definitely not be returning! For the $50 I paid for just myself it 100% was not at all worth the price. My co workers complained about the lack of attentiveness and poor food quality as well and said they won't be returning either. Usually cactus club is an A++ but they absolutely more than missed the mark on this night. So no thanks, I'll go to a much more reputable place that knows how to make properly cooked chicken and well seasoned truffle fries not just tossed under the heat lamp for a few seconds not even room temp fries 🍟
#nothankyou 😞","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTChYQLzDD-_sWCeaozWjveRAUsUuT4CBWbN2j&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Date night with my husband. I got the lemongrass prawns and he got the garden burger with Parmesan fries. No picture, but we also got the chocolate peanut butter bar which we love and have ordered several times before. Service was alright but not outstanding.

Edit: we’ve been back several times and always great food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNz5o-NfFrzlsDuL1toQAzF3vym_4Nh0sKHc_Lp&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Jordan Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW11-xeEA0Ih57ocfphXt0C50QwI614ll6t2qknklEqHoDt3aVy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Solid cactus club location; nice atmosphere and decor. Consistent and stable restaurant chain location if you’re looking for food in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7JfFoNjTGrrXQsFLHbl5e01TNdKb9RpDU_IFL&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Karl San Ramon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMltI1k0x7sCrxqWzfGjhhl5muphr65hDnGIRaggxIcR7yfMIR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cactus Club has a great atmosphere and excellent customer service. I highly recommend trying the Grilled Dijon Salmon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNl92y_vb_FdIj60kUcUGAjZPOYeXYYPKVGDMhf&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"KANVAS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIc7GQRe5cyMmMtBU7rwkkBMqSxMQC9wVOgxESX-9VBPO4cx_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Im not one to go chain restaurants, given it was my first time and was highly recommended by friends. Toronto your better not let me down your new location is next!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMA1QrmgM-GyOZ24ZLj9F_eDXwNVUXstwreB7rT&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"L V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbiBK61CfZsFrw4Y5hmNaYU_dtvifHPnmGFELAVcKqQqcdlg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We did not make a reservation but we did not have to wait too long to be seated. Love the combination of the spicy chicken and Pickles. The lettuce wraps were a little too sweet for my liking but it is a great portion size. The Truffle Parmesan Chicken is amazing. All in all it was a great meal, excellent service and ambience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQyUeOozUAESqYwdONgFOXK7yBuKkPRnZnhibN&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"MAY 매이 Elford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxJVIiA7BVVmzUGqT6sRzP7-hCdYJttIOnYMeIvWOWZPmq7cr7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Celebrated a birthday 🎂 and the birthday card on the table was a lovely touch. Our server was friendly and great!
No problem with ordering and food came out quick and perfect.
Even with someone who had a difficult dietary restriction, the server managed to accommodate my friend. She also managed to get my drink request done!
Thank you! Keep up the good work! Hope we can reserve again for our next visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipND9CuiRPSHeu1y7A29JkMA03atMeWruLWhVzkM&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-5-14"}]

[{"Name":"Brittany","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHTcuSM-4ly1uIP3q2-jgQ_2Vqi7GhBmGO9JykCcOlnN1NYOmqYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Came after sampling the Lavender Sour at Chickpea and being absolutely drawn in.

The experience as a whole was disappointing at the taproom: It might have been an off evening due to Halloween festivities/weather, but upon arriving, a few of the tap handles were sold out - Taps that would have made Moody Ales stand out amongst the others that do the usual IPAs and pales. Compared to the other taprooms themselves, Moody felt tight. Closely packed in families with little space or cohesion in the room.

I’d love to update my review when I come back to the row and try more beers/when it might be less crazy. There’s truly nothing like their Lavender Sour out there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJCYqqFkCQuwTHjZHQs2-VRILDRxidYTivcAxN&fid=0x0:0x2ab68beb4fa0d9d6"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Kayla Bell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPYYItX53_JFRw1bvGvWQbBS_a-Al_HMey-fawhYa_cPyuUqUv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visit this brewery regularly, and it’s been even better since the new leadership team has come in. The new food menu is fantastic, and their seasonal beer variety is always a winner along Brewery Row.

Most recently, we attended Taylor Swift trivia, and it was so well run. It was the first time I’ve attended one of their trivia nights, and it definitely won’t be the last.

The host was fantastic, even while having to deal with a table of self proclaimed SFU professors that weren’t there for trivia, but made sure to state their claim on a reserved table and be obnoxious and rude to the host and other guests. I digress.

Other than the blatant misogyny of the one man in the SFU group, the experience was amazing. Great beer, great staff, great atmosphere, great event. Can’t wait to visit again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwBfwAoIcn840TD4azZYI3oMf2OiWRXCxXf4fi&fid=0x0:0x2ab68beb4fa0d9d6"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Tony Sebastian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiWqdXCEwpIVB9StmiemuyGnyCJmr0IdMdtYRQU_cWFPEJXoA8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Moody Ales is and can be the only start to port moody beer crawl. Fantastic brewery!
Can’t say how much I love this place and the people!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9INWLwOIOj7qoDEEgRRPDIyHbZve3o9eGrWbb&fid=0x0:0x2ab68beb4fa0d9d6"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Adrienne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvS1YiBi1kAYmplCTkzo9NqyjbLMViYayHxaEQA-dKyQUyyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I came here specifically for the lobster roll, and it did not disappoint! Definitely coming back for the lobster rolls!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKMs6e5h77w4u1xXxlBZS3MsC1U8z0X1soWwD4&fid=0x0:0x2ab68beb4fa0d9d6"],"When":"2023-7-9"},{"Name":"L K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7gOAyi31eGNkFBxsrBMX35BqtBkhbQww42uWrb70nTnOgyUwd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent staff and beer selection to drink myself away as my kids do volleyball tryouts at harry Jerome sports centre near by. 🍺🍺🍺🤘","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOL_swPCE6GVMAcjhHyCITymYoTQCzu1oeRsfR7&fid=0x0:0x2ab68beb4fa0d9d6"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Christina Swanson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNWxyzlnDsWbzgDQ8_CWAvQAx_6I-ake3OPyqbMMREgPal9Ngk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friends & I love coming to the trivia nights at Moody Ales! The beermosa with the strawberry kiwi beer is great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Grant Truesdell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYnlna-_GRxIxqy6nGy2CX0YwzOYaR6NSIYfz0eWEQHv9tJ_uh=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Decent beer and staff.
